ote%20of%20Doe%2036.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPreska%20used%20the%20same%20language%20in%20her%20rulings%20for%20more%20than%20one-third%20of%20the%20Does%20on%20the%20list%20to%20describe%20their%20lack%20of%20objection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20she%20did%20not%20include%20that%20note%20in%20her%20ruling%20for%20Doe%20174%2C%20instead%20writing%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20interests%20that%20outweigh%20the%20presumption%20of%20access%20have%20been%20identified%20with%20specificity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20material%20should%20be%20unsealed%20in%20full%2C%26quot%3B%20Preska%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Trump%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EVictims%20talked%20about%20Trump%20as%20one%20of%20Epstein's%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unsealed%20documents%20are%20not%20all%20damning%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20unsealed%20documents%20the%20judge%20said%20named%20Doe%20174%20are%20from%20a%20deposition%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-told-victim-bill-clinton-likes-girls-young-deposition-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohanna%20Sjoberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20accused%20Epstein%20of%20rape%20and%20Prince%20Andrew%20of%20groping%20her%20(the%20British%20royal%20has%20denied%20the%20claims).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20deposition%2C%20Sjoberg%20denied%20massaging%20Trump%20at%20any%20of%20Epstein's%20properties.%20She%20also%20described%20flying%20to%20Atlantic%20City%20in%20Epstein's%20private%20jet%2C%20where%20they%20visited%20one%20of%20Trump's%20casinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJeffrey%20said%2C%20Great%2C%20we'll%20call%20up%20Trump%20and%20we'll%20go%20to%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20recall%20the%20name%20of%20the%20casino%2C%20but%20%E2%80%94%20we'll%20go%20to%20the%20casino%2C%26quot%3B%20Sjoberg%20recalled%20in%20the%20deposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20document%2C%20which%20was%20fully%20unsealed%20in%202022%2C%20is%20an%20already-public%202016%20New%20York%20Post%20article%20about%20the%20allegations%20against%20Epstein.%20It%20mentions%20that%20Trump%20and%20Epstein%20were%20friends%20and%20spent%20time%20at%20parties%20together%20in%20Palm%20Beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20other%20unsealed%20documents%20are%20motions%20and%20letters%20from%20lawyers%20representing%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Falan-dershowitz-david-boies-lawsuit-jeffrey-epstein-accuser-virginia-giuffre-case-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlan%20Dershowitz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Trump%20is%20mentioned%20in%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Epstein's%20name%20has%20been%20widely%20linked%20in%20the%20press%20with%20prominent%20individuals%20such%20as%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20attorneys%20wrote%20in%20a%20motion%20arguing%20that%20he%20should%20not%20be%20forced%20to%20testify%20in%20front%20of%20a%20jury%2C%20later%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BHis%20personal%20appearance%20at%20the%20trial%20of%20this%20case%20would%20predictably%20be%20the%20focus%20of%20massive%20media%20attention%2C%20of%20both%20the%20mainstream%20and%20gutter%20variety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225062%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alan%20Dershowitz.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61dc50fd4129ea0019f34a82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223452%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlan%20Dershowitz.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20unsealed%20document%2C%20from%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20Dershowitz%2C%20seeks%20to%20discredit%20one%20of%20his%20accusers%2C%20Sarah%20Ransome%2C%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20she%20has%20made%20unproven%20claims%20about%20possessing%20video%20footage%20of%20powerful%20people%20having%20sex%20with%20girls%20in%20Epstein's%20homes.%20Ransome%20had%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20a%20friend%20who%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20many%20girls%20that%20had%20sexual%20relations%20with%20Donald%20Trump%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20friend%20claimed%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20Trump%20in%20Epstein's%20Manhattan%20mansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%20how%20he%20kept%20going%20on%20about%20how%20he%20liked%20her%20'pert%20nipples%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ransome%20had%20said%2C%20purporting%20to%20cite%20a%20friend.%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20liked%20flicking%20and%20sucking%20her%20nipples%20until%20they%20were%20raw.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERansome%20later%20recanted%20her%20claims%20about%20having%20the%20video%20footage.%20In%20her%20book%20%26quot%3BSilenced%20No%20More%3A%20Surviving%20My%20Journey%20to%20Hell%20and%20Back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20he%20told%20the%20false%20story%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20insurance%20policy%2C%20though%20she%20maintained%20that%20%26quot%3BJeffrey%20kept%20a%20trove%20of%20surveillance%20on%20every%20person%20who%20had%20ever%20visited%20his%20properties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20absolutely%20terrified%20that%2C%20once%20I%20went%20public%20with%20my%20story%2C%20Jeffrey%20and%20Ghislaine%20would%20find%20and%20kill%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ransome%20wrote%20in%20her%20book.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20send%20them%20a%20message%20via%20the%20press%3A%20if%20you%20wage%20war%20on%20me%2C%20I%20will%20return%20fire%20by%20releasing%20my%20evidence.%20That%20would%20be%20my%20leverage%2C%20my%20way%20of%20protecting%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20of%20the%20nine%20documents%20naming%20Doe%20174%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20fully%20unsealed%2C%20the%20public%20docket%20includes%20versions%20with%20some%20redactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20see%20where%20Trump%20fits%20into%20them.%20They%20are%20all%20transcripts%20of%20depositions%20from%20Ransome%2C%20Giuffre%2C%20and%2