0track%20record%2C%20you%20should%20know%20that%20I%20have%20the%20skill%20to%20get%20people%20to%20succeed%20in%20fighting%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%20off%20with%20Modi%20in%202012-13%2C%20Kishor%20has%20worked%20with%20many%20political%20leaders%20across%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20achieved%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20success%20as%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20election%20manager.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20achieving%20success%20as%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20strategist%20and%20as%20a%20political%20leader%20of%20the%20people%20are%20two%20different%20ball%20games.%20There%20is%20no%20measuring%20scale%20other%20than%20elections%20to%20measure%20if%20Kishor%20can%20make%20a%20mark%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20Bihar%20and%20of%20India%20in%20general.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKishor%20has%20so%20far%20toured%2015%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%2038%20districts%20in%20the%2016%20months%20of%20his%20padyatra%2C%20but%20he%20still%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20establishing%20himself%20as%20a%20meaningful%20leader%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20election%20might%20give%20a%20hint%20about%20his%20fate%20and%20his%20prospects%20for%20transforming%20himself%20from%20an%20election%20manager%20to%20a%20political%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENalin%20Verma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704769258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08235742%2FPrashant-Kishor.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fp