Pranay%20Verma%2C%20was%20the%20first%20foreign%20ambassador%20to%20call%20on%20Hasina.%20He%20was%20followed%20by%20envoys%20from%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutan%2C%20Philippines%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20conspicuous%20absence%20of%20any%20congratulations%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20western%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Canadian%20high%20commission%20tweeted%20that%20it%20had%20not%20sent%20any%20election%20observer%20to%20Bangladesh.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20individual%20who%20identifies%20as%20a%20Canadian%20observer%20is%20acting%20independently.%20Their%20views%20have%20not%20been%20endorsed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20posted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Felection-2024%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fpolls-largely-free-and-fair-3513701%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20per%20Bangladesh%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20section%20of%20foreign%20observers%2C%20including%20Canadian%20lawmaker%20of%20Indian%20origin%2C%20Chandra%20Arya%20and%20his%20colleague%2C%20Senator%20Victor%20Oh%20congratulated%20%E2%80%9CBangladesh%20Election%20Commission%20on%20successfully%20conducting%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%E2%80%9D.%20The%20head%20of%20the%20Head%20of%20the%20Russian%20election%20monitoring%20delegation%20Andrey%20Y.%20Shuvot%20labelled%20the%20elections%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newagebd.net%2Farticle%2F222254%2Fmost-intl-observers-find-election-free-fair%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elegitimate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20sent%20a%20three%20member%20delegation%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20which%20issued%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2F15590-statement-of-the-3-member-international-observers-delegation-from-the-election-commission-of-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20visited%20a%20number%20of%20polling%20stations%20and%20have%20witnessed%20the%20polling%20process%20first%20hand.%20We%20saw%20citizens%20of%20Bangladesh%20exercising%20their%20electoral%20rights%20at%20these%20stations%20peacefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20also%20appreciated%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20efforts%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20its%20meticulous%20planning%20and%20arrangements%20made%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20election%20process%20and%20facilitating%20this%20visit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Election%20Expert%20Mission%20of%20the%20EU%2C%20joint%20technical%20assessment%20team%20from%20the%20International%20Republican%20Institute%20and%20National%20Democratic%20Institute%2C%20and%20election%20observers%20from%20the%20Commonwealth%20have%20yet%20to%20release%20their%20assessments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Bangladeshi%20media%2C%20there%20was%20large%20amounts%20of%20pessimism%20over%20the%20extremely%20low%20turnout%2C%20which%20indicated%20that%20most%20of%20the%20electorate%20felt%20that%20they%20had%20no%20choice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%2060%20percent%20of%20voters%20who%20have%20stayed%20away%20are%20not%20absentees.%20They%20are%20the%20face%20of%20disenfranchisement%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Bangladesh%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fnews%2Felection-more-form-substance-3513836%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Daily%20Star%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20an%20editorial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2F