20the%20best%20players%20our%20sport%20has%20ever%20seen.%20With%20his%20lightness%2C%20elegance%20and%20overview%2C%20he%20set%20standards%20on%20the%20pitch.%20His%20meticulousness%20and%20charisma%20as%20team%20manager%20and%20his%20energy%20and%20drive%20as%20head%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20organizing%20committee%20are%20unforgettable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFranz%20Beckenbauer%20leaves%20behind%20a%20great%20legacy%20for%20the%20DFB%20and%20football%20as%20a%20whole.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDFB%20vice%20president%20Hans-Joachim%20Watzke%20added%20that%20Beckenbauer%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20definitely%20the%20biggest%20German%20footballer%20of%20all%20time%2C%20and%20above%20all%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20men%20who%20I%20have%20known.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFranz%20Beckenbauer%2C%20one%20of%20European%20football%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20sons%2C%20has%20passed%20away%20aged%2078.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDer%20Kaiser%E2%80%9D%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20player%2C%20successful%20coach%20and%20popular%20pundit%20who%20shaped%20German%20football%20like%20no%20other.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrW12ArNnNh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FrW12ArNnNh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UEFA%20(%40UEFA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUEFA%2Fstatus%2F1744403806194970839%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bundesliga%20family%20is%20devastated%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Franz%20Beckenbauer.%20A%20true%20icon%2C%20then%2C%20now%2C%20and%20always.%20RIP%2C%20Der%20Kaiser%2C%E2%80%9D%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20Bundesliga%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELothar%20Matth%C3%A4us%2C%20who%20captained%20Germany%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%201990%2C%20hailed%20the%20late%20Beckenbauer%20as