3Cstrong%3EA%20storied%20career%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeckenbauer%20was%20one%20of%20just%20three%20people%20ever%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20both%20as%20a%20player%20and%20a%20coach%2C%20alongside%20the%20late%20Mario%20Zagallo%20of%20Brazil%20and%20France%E2%80%99s%20Didier%20Deschamps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20success%20with%20the%20national%20team%2C%20he%20earned%20numerous%20honours%20during%20his%20tenure%20at%20Bayern%20Munich%2C%20including%20three%20consecutive%20European%20Cups%20and%20the%20Intercontinental%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coaching%2C%20Beckenbauer%20moved%20into%20football%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20made%20headlines%20in%202016%20when%20was%20fined%20by%20FIFA%E2%80%99s%20ethics%20committee%20for%20failing%20to%20co-operate%20with%20an%20inquiry%20into%20corruption%20over%20the%20awarding%20of%20the%202018%20and%202022%20World%20Cups%20in%20Russia%20and%20Qatar%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffranz-beckenbauer-called-a-true-legend-in-global-tributes%2Fa-67921493%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704768502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09081354%2FScreenshot-2024-01-09-at-8.13.48%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Ffranz-beckenbauer-passes-away%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20German%20player%20was%20one%20of%20just%20three%20people%20ever%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20both%20as%20a%20player%20and%20a%20coach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Ffranz-beckenbauer-passes-away%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranji%20Trophy%3A%20Captain%20Yash%20Dhull%20sacked%20after%