ww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fmuslimmirror.com%2Feng%2Furus-at-dattatreya-baba-budangiri-dargah-in-ktaka-muslims-stay-away%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704787637059000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2yFHluXCtmTFhSX5J7ROqZ%5C%22%3Eplace%20is%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20called%20Baba%20Budangiri%20and%20Dattatreya%20Peetha.%20Before%201964%2C%20the%20shrine%20was%20revered%20by%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20It%20symbolised%20Sufi%20culture%20and%20unity%20of%20Hindu%20and%20Islam%20cultures.%20What%20was%20a%20pilgrimage%20spot%20for%20the%20two%20faiths%20has%20become%20a%20disputed%20site%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20dispute%20is%20in%20the%20court%2C%20but%20through%20this%20journey%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20succeeded%20in%20consolidating%20its%20base%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20southern%20state%2C%20and%20this%20matter%20has%20become%20a%20constant%20source%20for%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fwhy-bhagyalakshmi-temple-hyderabad-has-become-centre-bjps-campaign-138617%5C%22%3EBhagyalaxmi%20temple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20situated%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Charminar%20wall%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siasat.com%2Fhyderabad-is-the-bhagyalaxmi-temple-at-charminar-expanding-2435006%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20gradually%20expanding%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sow%20the%20seeds%20of%20discord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20near%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmaharashtra-chief-minister-eknath-shinde-haji-malang-dargah-kalyan-2484202-2024-01-04%5C%22%3EHaji%20Malang%20Dargah%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20brought%20into%20dispute%20and%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Rane%20is%20reviving%20the%20campaign%20to%20claim%20the%20dargah%20as%20the%20Hindu%20place%20of%20worship.%20The%20agitation%20was%20begun%20by%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20mentor%20Anand%20Dighe%20in%201982.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20communal%20tensions%20over%20the%20structure%2C%20which%20signifies%20the%20syncretic%20culture%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20occurred%20in%20the%201980s%20when%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Dighe%20started%20a%20protest%2C%20claiming%20it%20was%20located%20at%20the%20site%20of%20an%20old%20Hindu%20shrine%20belonging%20to%20Nath%20Panth%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adeex.in%2Fnews%2Fwhy-eknath-shinde-wants-to-liberate-maharashtras-centuries-old-haji-malang-dargah%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.adeex.in%2Fnews%2Fwhy-eknath-shinde-wants-to-liberate-maharashtras-centuries-old-haji-malang-dargah%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704787637059000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0cNuPIvG52slbCxEb5Dv5_%5C%22%3E%2C%20an%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20yogis.%20He%20claimed%20the%20shrine%20belonged%20to%20Hindus%20as%20it%20was%20the%20site%20of%20a%20700-year-old%20Machindranath%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20leaders%20started%20visiting%20the%20place%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20Urs.%20And%20that%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20tension.%20The%20matter%20is%20also%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism%20in%20Mumbai%20sponsored%20a%20fact-finding%20team%2C%20which%20also%20interviewed%20the%20trustee%20of%20the%20dargah%20Trust%2C%20Kashinath%20Gopal%20Ketkar%2C%20as%20per%20whom%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20sort%20of%20proof%2C%20either%20documentary%20or%20whatsoever%E2%80%9D%20that%20it%20was%20a%20temple%20of%20the%20Nath%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20presence%20of%20Muslims%20is%20declining%20during%20Urs%20because%20of%20this%20controversy%2C%20but%20people%20come%20later%20on%20all%20the%20year%20round.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20what%20he%20thought%20of%20the%20renaming%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20it%20and%20I%20am%20rather%20pained%20to%20feel%20such%20things%20are%20being%20fomented.%20It%20is%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcsss-isla.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FAttack-on-Syncretic-Culture-Haji-Malang.pdf%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fcsss-isla.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FAttack-on-Syncretic-Culture-Haji-Malang.pdf%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704787637059000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2loT0epghG42P0w0s8ZFN5%5C%22%3Eshrine%20belongs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Muslim%20Sufis%2C%20but%20his%20devotees%20cut%20across%20all%20the%20countries.%E2%80%9D%20He%20further%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20of%2040%20villages%20around%20the%20hill%20will%20continue%20to%20say%20Haji%20Malang%20because%20they%20have%20deep-rooted%20devotion%20towards%20the%20shrine%2C%20but%20those%20who%20have%20the%20mischievous%20intention%20will%20say%20whatever%20it%20suits%20them.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Hereditary%20Trustee%20also%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20good%20services%20to%20his%20devotee%20without%20any%20discomfort%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20research%20scholar%2C%20Rama%20Shyam%2C%20who%20did%20her%20doctoral%20research%20on%20the%20syncretic%20traditions%20of%20India%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20this%20dargah%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20January%208%2C%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Ketkar%20family%20has%20the%20records%20which%20show%20their%20association%20with%20the%20dargah%20for%20over%20360%20years.%20Regarding%20the%20history%20of%20the%20place%20of%20Haji%20Malang%20baba%20and%20various%20shrines%20that%20line%20the%20entire%20path%20from%20foothills%20to%20the%20top%2C%20there%20are%20stories%20in%20oral%20tradition%20which%20pass%20through%20the%20generations.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Baba%20Malang%20came%20here%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Medina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest%20reference%20to%20Malang%20Gad%20Hills%20dates%20back%20to%201774%20during%20the%20Anglo-Maratha%20war.%20The%20Thane%20Gazetteer%20of%201882%20does%20mention%20the%20Bawa%20Malang%20fair%20held%20in%20these%20hills%2C%20a%20fact%20also%20confirmed%20by%20the%20CSSS%20report%20cited%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deliberate%20attempts%20to%20create%20a%20dispute%20around%20the%20heritage%20structures%2C%20either%20to%20claim%20that%20they%20were%20Hindu%20places%20appropriated%20by%20Muslims%20and%20need%20to%20be%20reclaimed%2C%20is%20a%20time-tested%20method%20by%20sectarian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20replete%20with%20these%20sacred%20spaces%20visited%20by%20people%20of%20all%20religions.%20The%20interesting%20story%20about%20the%20pilgrims%20of%20Sabarimala%20temple%2C%20who%20first%20visit%20St.%20Sebastian%20Church%20and%20then%20go%20to%20the%20mosque%20of%20Wavar%2C%20showcase%20a%20longstanding%20point%20of%20syncretism%20in%20India%20that%20has%20endured%20for%20centuries.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20the%20menacing%20form%20taken%20by%20sectarian%20nationalism%2C%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fndmc-considers-demolition-of-delhis-sunehri-masjid-jamiat-ulama-i-hind-objects%5C%22%3ESunehri%20Bagh%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20being%20targeted%2C%20ostensibly%20in%20the%20name%20of%20traffic%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20strength%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20religious%20traditions%20are%20these%20spaces%20where%20people%20from%20different%20religions%20intermix.%20With%20the%20ascendance%20of%20communal%20politics%2C%20most%20of%20the%20dargahs%20are%20either%20being%20targeted%20and%20Sufis%20are%20being%20demonised.%20Sadly%20the%20very%20traditions%20of%20intermixing%20are%20being%20looked%20down%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniy