0of%20which%20were%20for%20similar%20offences%20%E2%80%93%20taken%20into%20consideration%20in%20his%20sentencing%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20The%20Straits%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20that%20the%20various%20bills%20with%20the%20hospitals%20have%20since%20been%20settled%2C%20and%20that%20Logeswaran%20has%20repaid%20his%20brother%20via%20instalments%20while%20his%20acquaintance%20did%20not%20wish%20for%20any%20restitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Public%20Prosecutor%20Chan%20Yi%20Cheng%20said%20Logeswaran%20and%20his%20acquaintance%2C%20who%20first%20met%20him%20at%20a%20temple%2C%20had%20not%20seen%20each%20other%20since%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Logeswaran%20would%20occasionally%20contact%20the%20acquaintance%20to%20borrow%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Logeswaran%20contacted%20the%20acquaintance%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20identity%20card%20and%20name%20card%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20could%20register%20him%20as%20a%20transport%20contractor%20with%20the%20hotel%20that%20he%20was%20working%20for%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20acquaintance%20sent%20photographs%20of%20his%20identity%20card%20and%20name%20card%2C%20Logeswaran%20did%20not%20contact%20him%20with%20any%20job%20opportunities%20at%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Logeswaran%20visited%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%20on%20eight%20occasions%20between%20April%2029%2C%202016%2C%20and%20March%206%2C%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20acquaintance's%20identity%20card%20number%20to%20the%20hospital%20staff%20for%20registration%2C%20Logeswaran%20consulted%20a%20doctor%20for%20his%20back%20pain%20fow%20which%20he%20was%20given%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELogeswaran%20incurred%20bills%20totalling%20SGD%20421.74%20for%20eight%20health%20issues.%20The%20acquaintance%2C%20who%20received%20multiple%20letters%20informing%20him%20of%20the%20outstanding%20medical%20bills%2C%20notified%20th