20are%20like-minded%20in%20their%20quest%20for%20democracy%20and%20respect%20for%20human%20rights.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20short-sightedness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20present%20government%20to%20really%20think%20that%20we%20can%20really%20try%20to%20not%20keep%20the%20age-old%20relationship%20that%20we%20have%20always%20had%20with%20India...%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20row%20was%20triggered%20last%20week%20as%20Maldives%20deputy%20minister%2C%20along%20with%20other%20cabinet%20members%20and%20government%20officials%2C%20made%20disparaging%20and%20unsavoury%20references%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20Lakshadweep%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Male%3A%20On%20the%20row%20over%20Maldives%20MP's%20post%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Former%20Maldives%20Defence%20Minister%20Mariya%20Ahmed%20Didi%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20India%20has%20been%20our%20911%20call%2C%20whenever%20we%20need%20it%2C%20we%20give%20a%20call%20and%20you%20all%20come%20to%20our%20rescue.%20That%20kind%20of%20a%20friend.%20When%20you%20see%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9X64vqwWwg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9X64vqwWwg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1744381715412328770%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20former%20Maldives%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20%26quot%3B...%20India%20has%20been%20our%20911%20call%2C%20whenever%20we%20need%20it%2C%20we%20give%20a%20call%20and%20you%20all%20come%20to%20our%20rescue.%20That%20kind%20of%20a%20friend.%20When%20you%20see%20such%20disparaging%20remarks%20about%20friends%20like%20this%2C%20it%20is%20sad%20for%20everyone%20concerned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20the%20age-old%20relationship%20with%20India%20and%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20negative%20impact%20of%20such%20remarks%20on%20the%20friendship%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Maldives%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20that%20considering%20our%20close%20friendship%2C%20neighboring%20status%2C%20and%20participation%20in%20the%20global%20community%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20uphold%20our%20international%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20the%20historical%20%26quot%3BIndia%20first%26quot%3B%20policy%20and%20hoped%20for%20its%20continuation%2C%20recognizing%20India%20as%20the%20nearest%20neighbor%20that%20has%20consistently%20provided%20support%20in%20times%20of%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20think%20as%20close%20friends%2C%20as%20neighbours%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20global%20community%2C%20and%20we%20would%20keep%20our%20international%20commitments%20and%20Maldives%20government%2C%20would%20keep%20our%20traditional%20foreign%20policy%20of%20being%20friends%20with%20everyone.%20We've%20always%20had%20an%20India%20first%20policy%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20they%20continue%20it%2C%20that%20they%20recognize%20that%20you're%20the%20closest%20neighbour%2C%20that%20you%20will%20be%20the%20people%20who%20have%20always%20come%20and%20will%20come%20in%20the%20future%20also%20when%20the%20need%20arises%20and%20to%20have%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20people%20because%20we%20have%20always%20gone%20to%20India%20for%20medical%20treatment%20as%20wel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20urged%20acknowledgment%20of%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20people%2C%20highlighting%20instances%20of%20seeking%20medical%20treatment%20in%20India%20and%20receiving%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20under%20Indian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20do%20not%20have%20the%20facility%20to%20attend%20to%20certain%20illnesses%20in%20Maldives.%20Even%20otherwise%20when%20we%20had%20the%20Covid%2C%20we%20got%20the%20vaccines%20also%20under%20Indian%20aid.%20We've%20had%20so%20much%20cooperation%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20We%20have%20cooperated%20with%20each%20other%20from%20time%20immemorial%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20feasible%20for%20us%20to%20even%20think%20that%20we%20can%20replace%20our%20closest%20neighbour...%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%202%2C%20PM%20Modi%20visited%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Lakshadweep%20and%20shared%20several%20pictures%2C%20including%20an%20'exhilarating%20experience'%20of%20him%20trying%20his%20hand%20at%20snorkelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%2C%20PM%20Modi%20shared%20pictures%20of%20the%20white%20beaches%2C%20the%20pristine%20blue%20skies%20and%20the%20ocean%20and%20tagged%20them%20with%20a%20message%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20embrace%20the%20adventurer%20in%20them%2C%20Lakshadweep%20has%20to%20be%20on%20your%20list.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20that%20has%20now%20been%20deleted%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20Deputy%20Minister%20of%20Youth%20Empowerment%2C%20Shiuna%2C%20made%20a%20mocking%20and%20disrespectful%20reference%20to%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20government%20on%20Sunday%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Minister%20Mariyam%20Shiuna's%20derogatory%20remarks%2C%20saying%20her%20opinion%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20government's%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20added%20that%20'appropriate%20action'%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20minister%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20social%20media%20firestorm%20over%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20added%20that%20it%20believes%20that%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20should%20be%20exercised%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%20and%20responsible%20manner%2C%20and%20in%20ways%20that%20do%20not%20spread%20hatred%2C%20negativity%2C%20and%20hinder%20close%20relationships%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20its%20international%20partners%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Indian%20troops%20presence%20in%20Maldives%2C%20the%20minister%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20never%20been%20a%20question%20of%20Indian%20troops%20being%20here%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%20They%20have%20been%20here%20to%20help%20us%20on%20our%20government's%20request.%20Several%20successive%20governments%20have%20requested%20that%20they%20come%20and%20help%20us...%20It%20has%20been%20helping%20us%20keep%20our%20citizens%20safe%2C%20and%20it's%20sad%20that%20we%20do%20not%20see%20it%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Maldives%20has%20never%20had%20the%20Indian%20troops%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense%20in%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20the%20defence%20cooperation%2C%20India%20has%20offered%20us%20technical%20support%20purely%20on%20a%20humanitarian%20basis%20to%20bring%20our%20people%20from%20the%20islands%20to%20Male.%20The%20equipment%20that%20was%20given%20to%20Maldives%20has%20always%20been%20there%20to%20help%20us%2C%20to%20assist%20us%20in%20the%20humanitarian%20evacuation%20of%20our%20people.%20The%20helicopters%20that%20were%20there...%20they%20are%20completely%20under%20the%20command%20and%20control%20of%20MNDF%20(Maldives%20National%20Defence%20Force).%20The%20MNDF%20tells%20them%20when%20to%20fly%20and%20how%20to%20fly%20and%20what%20to%20do%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704764760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fp8384mso_maldives-generic_625x300_08_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-has-been-our-911-call-maldive