0enjoy%20doing%20a%20longer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdigital-detox-phone-addiction-sabbath-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edigital%20detox%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20not%20realistic%20for%20her%20career%20as%20a%20writer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20even%2024%20hours%20without%20a%20phone%2C%20laptop%2C%20or%20screen%20of%20any%20kind%20helps%20both%20as%20a%20mental%20reset%20and%20as%20a%20way%20to%20identify%20triggers%20that%20keep%20you%20hooked%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20see%20at%20what%20point%20you're%20reaching%20for%20your%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%2C%26quot%3B%20Elefante%20said.%20She%20said%20email%20tends%20to%20be%20the%20one%20she%20always%20wants%20to%20check%20first%2C%20due%20to%20growing%20up%20with%20that%20technology%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20detoxes%2C%20she%20also%20learned%20how%20dependent%20she%20is%20on%20her%20phone%20in%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20an%20introvert%20at%20heart%2C%20anytime%20I%20had%20to%20do%20small%20talk%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20my%20least%20favorite%20thing%20in%20the%20entire%20world%2C%20I%20would%20put%20my%20hand%20on%20my%20back%20pocket%20looking%20for%20a%20phone%20that%20wasn't%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Set%20specific%20days%20to%20check%20social%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20smartphones%20and%20social%20media%20apps%20now%20track%20screen%20time%20and%20send%20reminders%20to%20close%20out%2C%20Elefante%20never%20uses%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20timers%20don't%20work%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20make%20me%20feel%20worse.%20I%20just%20snooze%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20hacks%20is%20only%20allowing%20herself%20to%20check%20Instagram%20once%20every%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20OK%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20miss%20some%20potential%20contacts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20since%20it's%20common%20for%20friends%20to%20share%20memes%20over%20social%20media%20DMs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Elefante%2C%20being%20slower%20to%20respond%20is%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20getting%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-to-break-social-media-addiction%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoff%20of%20the%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Make%20meaningful%20swaps%20for%20smartphones%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20why%20taking%20breaks%20from%20technology%20is%20so%20difficult%20is%20because%20it%20feels%20like%20you're%20taking%20something%20away%20instead%20of%20adding%20something%20new%2C%20Elefante%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20create%20a%20vacuum%20where%20it%20was%20because%20you're%20going%20to%20spend%20your%20time%20feeling%20anxious%2C%20like%20you're%20missing%20out%20on%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20have%20to%20put%20something%20in%20its%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElefante%20recommends%20making%20swaps%20like%20reading%20a%20physical%20book%20on%20your%20commute%20instead%20of%20on%20a%20tablet%20or%20doing%20crosswords%20with%20a%20pen%20and%20paper%20instead%20of%20playing%20online%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20picked%20up%20a%20camera%20again%2C%20an%20actual%20film%20camera%2C%20and%20started%20to%20go%20on%20walks%2C%26quot%3B%20Elefante%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20made%20it%20so%20I%20didn't%20feel%20stressed%20and%20anxious%20when%20I%20was%20without%20my%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Get%20comfortable%20with%20saying%20no%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElefante%20said%20that%20setting%20these%20boundaries%20can%20be%20hard%2C%20given%20how%20enticing%20social%20media%20is%20designed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pull%20is%20very%2C%20very%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20constant%20struggle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20keeps%20her%20focused%20on%20her%20goal%20is%20knowing%20what's%20most%20important%20to%20her.%20After%20accomplishing%20her%20dream%20of%20writing%20a%20book%2C%20she%20made%20compromises%20on%20how%20she%20would%20promote%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20no%20to%20more%20things%20than%20you%20can%20possibly%20imagine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-staying-off-phone-limiting-screen-time-cut-down-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704755177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65987c2c1c5c7b8c9a0e8f61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-staying-off-phone-limiting-screen-time-cut-down-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20media%20consultant%20experienced%20brain%20fog%20and%20memory%20loss%20from%20being%20online%20too%20much.%20She%20does%20these%204%20things%20to%20stay%20off%20her%20phone%20and%20limit%20her%20screen%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A92%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-staying-off-phone-limiting-screen-time-cut-down-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20best%20moments%20from%20the%202024%20Golden%20Globes%20that%20you%20didn't%20see%20on%20television%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meryl%20Streep%20kissing%20Amanda%20Seyfried%20at%20the%202024%20Golden%20Globes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c04d01c5c7b8c9a0ebd6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%