20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20arrogance.%20Their%20party%20turned%20the%20by-poll%20into%20a%20joke%20where%20the%20candidate%20could%20be%20appointed%20as%20a%20minister%20without%20being%20elected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET.T.%20held%20the%20portfolios%20of%20the%20minority%20and%20waqf%20department%2C%20the%20agricultural%20marketing%20department%20and%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3ENahar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Canal)%20department.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20T.T.%20had%20also%20served%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Vasundhara%20Raje-led%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20his%20defeat%20in%20the%20Karanpur%20by-poll%2C%20BJP%20state%20president%20C.P.%20Joshi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20will%20review%20the%20reasons%20for%20TT%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20the%20by-poll.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBhajanlalBjp%2Fstatus%2F1744390152024428843%5C%22%3EChief%20minister%20Sharma%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20T.T.%20had%20%E2%80%9Chappily%20accepted%20the%20mandate%20and%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20of%20minister%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20state%20chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20showed%20that%20a%20government%20can%20make%20someone%20a%20minister%2C%20but%20not%20an%20MLA%2C%20for%20which%20you%20need%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20public%20has%20rejected%20the%20unconstitutional%20move%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20poll.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Election%20Commission%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20any%20action%20in%20the%20matter.%20But%20the%20people%20gave%20their%20reply.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20also%20lodged%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20December%2031%20following%20T.T.%E2%80%99s%20oath%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanher