ppen%20there%20at%20any%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20accused%20the%20former%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20of%20taking%20several%20anti-Dalit%20decisions%2C%20which%20included%20constructing%20an%20over%20bridge%20in%20front%20of%20the%20BSP%20office%20in%20Lucknow%20from%20where%20%26quot%3Bconspiratorial%20anarchist%20elements%26quot%3B%20could%20harm%20the%20party%20office%2C%20staff%20and%20the%20national%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20she%20could%20get%20it%20demolished%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20with%20which%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bhand%20in%20glove%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bridge%20was%20built%20following%20all%20rules%20after%20obtaining%20NOC%20from%20the%20Railways%20and%20Defence%20ministries%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20who%20had%20dedicated%20the%20bridge%20to%20the%20public%20in%202014%20when%20he%20was%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20BSP%20chief's%20request%20to%20shift%20her%20party%20office%20because%20of%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20SP%20president%20retorted%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20has%20stopped%20them%2C%20they%20are%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20BJP.%20If%20the%20BSP%20leadership%20feels%20that%20its%20security%20is%20in%20danger%20then%20it%20should%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20get%20this%20bridge%20demolished.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20many%20bulldozers%20and%20can%20bring%20it%20down.%20I%20am%20prepared%20for%20it%20if%20the%20BJP%20listens%20to%20Mayawati%20ji%2C%20we%20have%20no%20complaints%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20further%20said%20former%20chief%20minister%20N%20D%20Tiwari%20used%20to%20take%20keen%20interest%20when%20it%20was%20being%20constructed%20and%20was%20also%20present%20at%20its%20inauguration.%20%26quot%3BWill%20they%20blame%20ND%20Tiwari%20also%3F%20Who%20all%20will%20be%20blamed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20following%20Mayawati's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBSP%20chief%20Ms%20Mayawati's%20doubt%20on%20the%20SP%20regarding%20her%20security%20proves%20that%20the%20character%20of%20the%20SP%20has%20still%20not%20changed.%20The%20SP%20government%20had%20made%20a%20nefarious%20attempt%20to%20murder%20Behen%20Mayawati%20in%20the%20guest%20house%20incident.%20The%20government%20has%20always%20been%20alert%20regarding%20the%20safety%20of%20Mayawati%20and%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20the%20previous%20SP%20government%20had%20generated%20much%20heat%20as%20the%20BSP%20leaders%20had%20vehemently%20protested%20against%20its%20construction%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20a%20security%20threat%20to%20Mayawati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20over%20bridge%20posed%20a%20threat%20by%20exposing%20Mayawati's%20bungalow%20at%20Mall%20Avenue%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BSP%20office%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%20said%20that%20the%20BSP%20had%20to%20shift%20the%20statues%20of%20many%20personalities%20to%20her%20residence%20due%20to%20security%20problems%2C%20adding%20that%20given%20the%20insecurity%2C%20the%20party%20had%20to%20shift%20important%20meetings%20from%20the%20party%20office%20to%20her%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20chief%20said%20that%20this%20would%20also%20help%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20deal%20strictly%20with%20the%20anti-Dalit%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BSP%20makes%20a%20special%20request%20to%20the%20UP%20government%20to%20make%20arrangements%20at%20a%20safe%20place%20somewhere%20else%20instead%20of%20the%20current%20party%20state%20office%20otherwise%20any%20untoward%20incident%20can%20happen%20here%20at%20any%20time.%20Besides%2C%20the%20party%20also%20demands%20that%20the%20government%20should%20deal%20strictly%20with%20anti-Dalit%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20requesting%20for%20her%20party%20office%20to%20be%20shifted%2C%20Mayawati%20recalled%20the%20unpleasant%20incident%20of%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20house%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20June%202%2C%201995%2C%20when%20Mayawati%20had%20withdrawn%20support%20from%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agitated%20Samajwadi%20Party%20workers%20had%20post%20this%20attacked%20Mayawati%20at%20the%20guest%20house%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20besides%20hurling%20abuses%20at%20her%20allegedly%20cut%20off%20the%20electricity%20and%20water%20supply%20of%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20lawmaker%20Brahm%20Dutt%20Dwivedi%20had%20rescued%20her%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%20launched%20a%20vitriolic%20attack%20on%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20not%20only%20being%20anti-most%20backward%20classes%20but%20also%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-Dalit%20party%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20chief%20said%20that%20her%20party%20tried%20to%20change%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20anti-Dalit%20%26quot%3Bchal%2C%20charita%20and%20chehra%26quot%3B%20after%20an%20alliance%20with%20it%20in%20the%20last%20general%20elections%2C%20but%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%20returned%20to%20its%20anti-Dalit%20and%20casteist%20agenda%20after%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%20said%20whenever%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20chief%20talks%20about%20an%20alliance%2C%20his%20first%20condition%20is%20maintaining%20distance%20with%20the%20BSP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704733020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fja6ma2tk_mayawati-pti_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawati-requests-up-government-to-shift-party-office-to-safe-place-4824913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BSP%20chief%20Mayawati%20on%20Monday%20asked%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government%20to%20shift%20her%20party's%20state%20office%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%26quot%3B%20place%20to%20prevent%20the%20occurrence%20of%20any%20untoward%20incident%20that%20%26quot%3Bcan%20happen%20there%20at%20any%20time%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawati-requests-up-government-to-shift-party-office-to-safe-place-4824913%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawati-requests-up-government-to-shift-party-office-to-safe-place-4824913%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawati-requests-up-government-to-shift-party-office-to-safe-place-4824913%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhen%20One%20Is%20No%20Longer%20Chief%20Minister...%26quot%3B%3A%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20has%20remarked%20that%20photos%20disappear%20from%20hoardings%20like%20the%20%26quot%3Bhorns%20from%20a%20donkey's%20head%26quot%3B%20when%20one%20is%20no%20longer%20holding%20a%20top%20post%2C%20comments%20coming%20after%20he%20missed%20out%20on%20a%20fifth%20term%20in%20office%20despite%20his%20party%20BJP%20posting%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20the%20November%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20stalwart%20said%20life%20is%20filled%20with%20joy%20when%20one%20sets%20a%20goal%20to%20work%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20was%20addressing%20a%20function%20of%20Brahma%20Kumaris%2C%20a%20spiritual%20movement%2C%20in%20the%20Neelbad%20area%20of%20Bhopal%20on%20Sunday%20and%20a%20video%20clip%20of%20his%20speech%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLife%20is%20filled%20with%20joy%20when%20we%20set%20a%20goal%20to%20do%20work%20for%20others.%20I%20still%20don't%20have%20time.%20I%20am%20constantly%20busy.%20It%20is%20good%20that%20we%20are%20getting%20a%20chance%20to%20work%20away%20from%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20four-term%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20maintained%20people%20active%20in%20politics%20also%20do%20good%20work%20with%20dedication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20leaders%20like%20Modi%20ji%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi)%20who%20live%20for%20the%20country.%20But%20there%20are%20many%20who%20see%20colours.%20If%20you%20are%20a%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20(such%20people%20say)%20'bhaisahab%20your%20feet%20and%20hands%20are%20like%20a%20lotus'.%20But%20when%20one%20is%20no%20longer%20(on%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post)%2C%20(his)%20photos%20disappear%20from%20hoardings%20like%20the%20horns%20from%20a%20donkey's%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2064-year-old%20BJP%20leader%20stepped%20down%20as%20chief%20minister%20last%20month%20and%20made%20way%20for%20his%20party%20colleague%20Mohan%20Yadav%20to%20take%20over%20the%20top%20post%20after%20the%20saffron%20party%20recorded%20a%20comprehensive%20win%20in%20the%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%20on%20Monday%20called%20on%20Chouhan%20at%20the%20latter's%20residence%2C%20which%20he%20has%20named%20%26quot%3BMama%20Ka%20Ghar%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20the%20state%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20during%20his%20long%20stint%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20implemented%20several%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20for%20girls%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20discuss%20these%20schemes.%20We%20will%20take%20all%20these%20schemes%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%2C%20addressing%20a%20gathering%20at%20Shahganj%20town%20under%20his%20assembly%20constituency%20Budhni%20in%20Sehore%20district%2C%20had%20remarked%20that%20sometimes%20one%20ends%20up%20in%20%26quot%3Bvanvas%26quot%3B%20(exile)%20while%20waiting%20for%20%26quot%3Brajtilak%26quot%3B%20(coronation).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704732600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fqf3h56m8_shivraj-chouhan-shraddh-poster_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-one-is-no-longer-chief-minister-photos-disappear-from-hoardings-like-horns-from-donkey-head-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4824596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20has%20remarked%20that%20photos%20disappear%20from%20hoardings%20like%20the%20%26quot%3Bhorns%20from%20a%20donkey's%20head%26quot%3B%20when%20one%20is%20no%20longer%20holding%20a%20top%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-one-is-no-longer-chief-minister-photos-disappear-from-hoardings-like-horns-from-donkey-head-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4824596%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-one-is-no-longer-chief-minister-photos-disappear-from-hoardings-like-horns-from-donkey-head-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4824596%2Famp%