e%20result%3A%20no%20headway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20suffered%20a%20string%20of%20losses%20in%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20state%20polls%2C%20is%20pushing%20to%20get%2010%20seats%20(which%20includes%20the%20two%20it%20won%20in%202019%20polls).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20with%20Trinamool%20will%20focus%20on%20these%20seats%2C%20party%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20Trinamool%20insists%20that%20it%20cannot%20spare%20more%20than%20two%20seats%20as%20the%20Congress%20won%20those%20many%20the%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grand%20old%20party%20sources%20say%20they%20too%20can%20question%20the%20Trinamool%20about%20the%2018%20seats%20that%20it%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20won%2022%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20two%20(Behrampore%20and%20Malda%20South)%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20secured%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202021%20Bengal%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20win%20a%20single%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20are%20also%20marred%20by%20the%20war%20of%20words%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20grand%20old%20party%20won't%20beg%20for%20seats%20from%20the%20Trinamool%26quot%3B.%20It%20drew%20a%20sharp%20and%20swift%20response%20from%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20%26quot%3BBadmouthing%20alliance%20partners%20and%20seat%20sharing%20can't%20go%20hand%20in%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20cautioned%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chowdhury%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20Bengal's%20ruling%20party%20of%20being%20busy%20%26quot%3Bserving%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20strengthening%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20criticised%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20for%20making%20%26quot%3Bcallous%20remarks%26quot%3B%20and%20cautioned%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20to%20rein%20in%20their%20state%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20an%20umbrella%20group%20of%20like-minded%20parties%20to%20take%20on%20BJP%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20firm-up%20the%20seat%20sharing%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20there%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20the%20TMC%20will%20fight%20and%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20Remember%2C%20in%20Bengal%2C%20only%20TMC%20can%20teach%20a%20lesson%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20not%20any%20other%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20late%20last%20month%20at%20a%20gathering%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704732360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Fbanfolds_congress-flag-650_625x300_03_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-eyes-10-bengal-seats-downplays-trinamools-2-seat-offer-sources-4824733%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20and%20Trinamool%20are%20caught%20in%20fraught%20negotiations%20over%20the%20seat-sharing%20formula%20for%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections.%20Both%20parties%20holding%20firm%20in%20their%20demands%2C%20say%20sources.%20The%20result%3A%20no%20headway.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-eyes-10-bengal-seats-downplays-trinamools-2-seat-offer-sources-4824733%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-eyes-10-bengal-seats-downplays-trinamools-2-seat-offer-sources-4824733%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-eyes-10-bengal-seats-downplays-trinamools-2-seat-offer-sources-4824733%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arbitral%20tribunal%20asks%20AAI%20to%20refund%20annual%20fees%20to%20Adani-owned%20MIAL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704731282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https