%20Schumacher%20household.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20in%20European%20Media%20Michael%20Schumacher's%20daughter%20Gina%20will%20get%20married%20to%20her%2027-year-old%20boyfriend%20Iain%20Bethke%20later%20this%20year.%20%C2%A0According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.si.com%2Ffannation%2Fracing%2Ff1briefings%2Fnews%2Fmichael-schumacher-family-planning-celebration-as-daughter-ties-the-knot-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESports%20Illustrated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20wedding%20ceremony%20will%20take%20at%20a%20villa%20in%20Majjorca%2C%20Spain%2C%20purchased%20by%20Corinna%20Schumacher%2C%20Michael's%20wife%2C%20from%20Real%20Madrid%20president%20Florentino%20Perez%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20world%20champions%20Sebastian%20Vettel%2C%20who%20close%20to%20Schumacher%20and%20his%20family%2C%20recently%20revealed%20that%20the%20F1%20legend%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20doing%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchumacher's%20lawyer%2C%20Felix%20Damm%2C%20however%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20former%20F1%20driver's%20family%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20make%20his%20final%20health%20report%20public%20due%20to%20privacy%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20always%20about%20protecting%20private%20things.%20We%20considered%20whether%20a%20final%20report%20about%20Michael's%20health%20could%20be%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20this%2C%3A%20Damm%20told%20German%20media%20outlet%20LTO%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20SI.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamm%20also%20stated%20that%20Schumacher's%20family%20would%20have%20come%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20media%20to%20release%20timely%20health%20updates%2C%20had%20they%20released%20the%20final%20health%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20the%20end%20of%20it%20and%20there%20would%20have%20had%20to%20be%20constantly%20updated%20'water%20level%20reports'%20and%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20up%20to%20the%20family%20when%20the%20media%20interest%20in%20the%20story%20stopped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20%5Bthe%20media%5D%20could%20pick%20up%20on%20such%20a%20report%20again%20and%20again%20and%20as%20'and%20what%20does%20it%20look%20like%20now%3F'%20one%2C%20two%2C%20three%20months%20or%20years%20after%20the%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20then%20wanted%20to%20take%20action%20against%20this%20reporting%2C%20we%20would%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20argument%20of%20voluntary%20self-disclosure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704726480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F42t9tapg_schumacher-son-daughter_625x300_08_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Fjoy-in-michael-schumacher-household-10-years-after-f1-greats-skiing-accident-reason-is-4824269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20December%2029%2C%202013%2C%20Michael%20Schumacher%20suffered%20a%20life-threatening%20injury%20while%20skiing%20in%20the%20French%20ski%20resort%20of%20Meribel%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Fjoy-in-michael-schumacher-household-10-years-after-f1-greats-skiing-accident-reason-is-4824269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Fjoy-in-michael-schumacher-household-10-years-after-f1-greats-skiing-accident-reason-is-4824269%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Fjoy-in-michael-schumacher-household-10-years-after-f1-greats-skiing-accident-reason-is-4824269%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20Teabags%20Release%20Plastic%3F%20Two%20Friends%20Fight%20The%20Damage%20With%20100%25%20Biodegradable%20%E2%80%98Bagless%E2%80%99%20Tea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20morning%2C%20our%20thoughts%20often%20turn%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3