trong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20held%20their%20first%20formal%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%20(January%208)%20to%20discuss%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20under%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20said%20that%20a%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20reached%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20national%20alliance%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20including%20convenor%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20and%20former%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20by%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20delegation%20included%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sandeep%20Pathak%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20and%20MLA%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Wasnik%20said%20that%20discussions%20were%20held%20on%20seat%20sharing%20as%20well%20as%20various%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20and%20that%20a%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20very%20good%20meeting.%20Senior%20AAP%20leaders%20were%20sent%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20for%20holding%20discussions%20with%20us%20on%20behalf%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20National%20Alliance%20Committee%20formed%20by%20the%20Congress%20president%20held%20discussions%20with%20AAP%20leaders%20for%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20on%20different%20issues%20relating%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20decided%20to%20hold%20further%20discussions%20and%20a%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20upcoming%20days.%20Discussion%20covered%20various%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasnik%20did%20not%2C%20however%2C%20divulge%20details%20on%20any%20seat-sharing%20agreements%20that%20were%20reached%20or%20the%20seats%20that%20were%20under%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20proper%20to%20reveal%20what%20transpired%20during%20the%20discussions.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20some%20time.%20We%20have%20already%20decided%20to%20contest%20elections%20together.%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20are%20a%20strong%20and%20important%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lovely%20said%20that%20the%20discussion%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpreliminary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20a%20preliminary%20meeting%20today%20and%20the%20seat%20sharing%20will%20be%20discussed%20when%20we%20meet%20again%20in%20maybe%20two%20days%20or%20within%20the%20next%20week.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20positive%20meeting%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20comes%20amid%20murmurs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-bjp-responsible-for-making-delhi-the-most-polluted-capital-congresss-arvinder-singh-lovely%5C%22%3Ediscontent%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20state%20units%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20have%20however%20said%20that%20the%20differences%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famid-disagreements-over-state-polls-congress-and-aap-say-india-alliance-is-for-national-election%5C%22%3Enot%20at%20the%20national%20level.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20complete%20unity%20and%20we%20are%20positive%20that%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20will%20be%20finalised%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bharadwaj%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%3A%20On%20AAP-%20Congress%20meeting%20over%20seat%20sharing%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%202024%2C%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20absolutely%20positive%20that%20seats%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20be%20finalised%20soon.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWSACLWQhp8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FWSACLWQhp8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1744337351550394855%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20despite%20state-level%20differences%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20unit%20will%20abide%20by%20the%20high%20command%E2%80%99s%20decision%20on%20working%20with%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%20also%20said%20that%20the%20differences%20with%20the%20AAP%20are%20relating%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20not%20at%20the%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20conflicts%20with%20AAP%20are%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government.%20They%20have%20also%20decided%20to%20come%20together%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20along%20with%20Congress.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20alliance%20will%20be%20decided%20later%20including%20seats.%20I%20am%20hoping%20that%20if%20an%20alliance%20happens%20then%20its%20details%20should%20be%20decided%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20so%20that%20we%20can%20also%20prepare%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5