0months%2C%20unwanted%20incidents%20took%20place%20on%20some%20days%2C%20not%20for%20the%20whole%20eight%20months.%20Three-four%20months%20were%20peaceful%20and%20silent.%20The%20violence%20during%20the%20new%20year%20was%20between%20the%20state%20security%20forces%20and%20militants%2C%20not%20between%20two%20communities.%20Now%2C%20the%20dimension%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20changed%20to%20state%20forces%20fighting%20against%20militants%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20remove%20the%20state%20police%20from%20Moreh%20and%20keep%20only%20central%20forces.%20They%20have%20alleged%20the%20police%20of%20attacking%20Kuki%20civilians.%20The%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20those%20attacking%20the%20state%20police%20commandos%20were%20hill-based%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20called%20for%20ending%20the%20Free-Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%20on%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%2C%20which%20allows%20people%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20border%20to%20travel%20over%2015%20km%20without%20papers%20in%20each%20other's%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBorder%20fencing%20is%20a%20must.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20cancel%20the%20FMR.%20Of%20course%2C%20people%20should%20come.%20Follow%20the%20rules%2C%20get%20paperwork%20as%20is%20done%20in%20any%20international%20travel.%20But%20right%20now%20there%20is%20no%20system%20in%20place%2C%20no%20checks%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20said%20they%20suspect%20the%20involvement%20of%20foreign%20mercenaries%20in%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20been%20doing%20to%20restore%20full%20normalcy%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20are%20themselves%20trying%20to%20restore%20peace.%20From%20the%20government%20side%20also%20we%20are%20trying%20our%20best%20with%20the%20guidance%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Both%20sides%20have%20been%20talking%20and%20discussions%20happening%20through%20proper%20channels.%20I%20can't%20disclose%20everything.%20Total%20normalcy%20will%20be%20restored%20very%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20government%20will%20give%20Rs%201%20lakh%20each%20to%20all%20displaced%20people%20in%2010%20days%20so%20that%20they%20can%20meet%20their%20immediate%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20blamed%20several%20successive%20governments%20in%20the%20past%20for%20the%20current%20crisis.%20%26quot%3BHad%20the%20leaders%20back%20in%201947-49%20during%20the%20merger%20given%20some%20attention%2C%20this%20problem%20would%20not%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20border%20is%20398%20km%20long.%20Some%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border%20share%20some%20ethnic%20ties.%20Had%20the%20fencing%20been%20done%20well%20decades%20ago%20and%20a%20pass%20system%20developed%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20influx%20would%20not%20have%20grown%20so%20big.%20The%20Centre%20in%20those%20early%20years%20left%20Manipur%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20border%20is%20guarded%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20but%20they%20are%20doing%20two%20jobs%20-%20guarding%20the%20border%20and%20carrying%20out%20counter-insurgency%20operations.%20They%20are%20stationed%2010-20%20km%20inside%20from%20the%20border.%20On%20top%20of%20this%2C%20there%20is%20the%20Free-Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%2C%20which%20allows%20people%20from%20across%20the%20border%20to%20come%20for%20several%20kilometres%20without%20any%20checks.%20So%20think%2C%20they%20are%20the%20same%20tribe%2C%20same%20community%2C%20same%20language%2C%20same%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20ever%20thought%20about%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20no%20one.%20It%20is%20only%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20came%20that%20we%20saw%20development%20and%20security%20in%20this%20region.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20previous%20governments%20-%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20about%20other%20states%20-%20left%20Manipur%20on%20its%20own.%20Whatever%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20because%20of%20the%20inaction%20by%20the%20previous%20governments%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20180%20have%20died%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20in%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20that%20began%20on%20May%203%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704717900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fi8jpm8o8_n-biren-singh-ndtv_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nature%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20shifted%20from%20clashes%20between%20two%20communities%20to%20attacks%20by%20insurgents%20on%20security%20forces%20now%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Four%20Decades%20of%20Milking%20a%20Deity%20in%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152731%2F415264154_1140688944092003_6108166337890878806_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20four-decade%20long%20history%20of%20the%20agitation%20for%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20place%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20made%20a%20profoundly%20indicative%20disclosure%20on%20January%2011%2C%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMade%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20a%20day%20in%20New%20Delhi%20after%20his%20release%20from%20custody%2C%20it%20was%20possibly%20aimed%20at%20deflecting%20the%20accusation%20of%20being%20among%20those%20directly%20responsible%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20serve%20as%20a%20reminder%2C%20Advani%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flalu-yadav-on-why-and-how-he-arrested-lk-advani-on-october-23-1990-1784734%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20December%208%2C%201992%2C%20well%20after%20dust%20from%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%E2%80%99s%20rubbles%20settled%20down%20and%20rioting%20erupted%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20India.%20He%20was%20released%20on%20January%2010%2C%201993%2C%20following%20a%20court%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20addressing%20journalists%2C%20he%20clarified%20that%20the%20campaign%20was%20not%20merely%20aimed%20at%20constructing%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20place%20of%20the%20medieval%20mosque.%20Instead%2C%20its%20objective%20was%20to%20arose%20among%20Indians%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cawareness%20of%20cultural%20nationalism.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20agitation%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98liberation%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20was%20a%20mere%20vehicle%20for%20propagating%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20imagination%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccountry%20and%20its%20people%E2%80%9D.%20The%20intention%20was%20to%20secure%20acceptance%20for%20the%20saffron%20fold%E2%80%99s%20viewpoint%20regarding%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20position%20of%20the%20minorities%20in%20the%20country%20and%20their%20response%20to%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majority%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20these%20notions%20were%20fairly%20Greek%20then%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20Indians%2C%20the%20movement%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20and%20publicists%20played%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20emotions%20by%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9Crestoration%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbirth-place%20of%20Bhagwan%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%E2%80%98liberation%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20child%20Ram%20from%20the%20jail%20that%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20projected%20as%2C%20became%20a%20common%20talking-point%20of%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20mosque%20to%20exist%20at%20that%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20site%E2%80%9D%2C%20was%20little%20but%20blasphemous.%20To%20stir%20up%20passions%20of%20Hindus%2C%20repeated%20calls%20were%20made%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20mythical-hero%20turned%20deity.%20In%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20name%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20support%20programmes%20and%20campaigns%20being%20waged%20by%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20organisations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20ensuring%20that%20people%20turned%20out%20in%20large%20numbers%20for%20the%20first%20yatra%20of%20the%20movement%2C%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janki%20Rath%20Yatra%20in%20September-October%201984%2C%20to%20the%20impending%20celebrations%20on%20January%2022%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20long%20sequence%20of%20%E2%80%98events%E2%80%99.%20The%20sole%20aim%20of%20all%20this%20was%20to%20widen%20the%20political%20base%20of%20BJP%20and%20affiliated%20organisations%2C%20by%20figuratively%20speaking%2C%20%E2%80%98milking%20Ram.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fayodhyatimeline%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAfter%2520the%2520demolition%2520of%2520the%2Cdestroyed%252C%2520including%252023%2520local%2520mosques.%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Ayodhya%3A%20Once%20There%20Was%20A%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20onset%2C%20it%20must%20be%20recalled%20that%20while%20the%20Ayodhya-Ram%20temple-Babri%20Masjid%20issue%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20public%20contestation%20in%20the%20late%201940s%20and%20immediately%20after%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20desecration%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20Dec%2022-23%2C%201949%2C%20the%20issue%20thereafter%2C%20receded%20to%20the%20background.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%201950s%2C%20an%20impromptu%20local%20committee%20supervised%20worship%20of%20child%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20idol%20and%20the%20matter%20faded%20from%20public%20discourse.%20Even%20after%20a%20fresh%20push%20was%20given%20to%20Hindu%20communalist%20ideas%20through%20a%20series%20of%20programmes%20staring%20with%20the%20Ekatmata%20Yagna%20in%201983%2C%20secular%20groups%20failed%20to%20comprehend%20interconnections%20between%20seemingly%20disparate%20initiatives%20of%20the%20orchestrated%20ideological%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Shri%20Ram%20Janki%20Rath%20Yatra%20from%20Sitamarhi%20in%20Bihar%20was%20synonymous%20with%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Mukti%20Yagna%20Samiti%20and%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20separate%20one%20from%20the%20other.%20The%20latter%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20established%20after%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20hosted%20a%20Dharam%20Sansad%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Vigyan%20Bhavan%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%20in%20the%20initial%20years%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20focus%20of%20political%20discourse%20then%20was%20dominated%20by%20religious%20extremism%20in%20Punjab%20and%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98anti-outsider%E2%80%99%20Assam%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsequently%2C%20when%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janki%20Rath%20Yatra%20arrived%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%201984%2C%20no%20one%20joined%20the%20dots%2C%20which%20if%20done%2C%20could%20have%20pointed%20to%20Hindu%20right-wing%20forces%E2%80%99%20emerging%20strategy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20their%20adversaries%20took%20note%20that%20the%20truck%20on%20which%20large%20statues%20of%20Ram%20and%20Sita%20were%20displayed%2C%20was%20emblazoned%20with%20banners%20proclaiming%20the%20slogan%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20From%20the%20movement%E2%80%99s%20infancy%2C%20it%20was%20a%20religio%2Fcultural-nationalist%20movement%20and%20not%20merely%20a%20religious%20demand.%20The%20claim%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple%20and%20erasure%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20framed%20within%20the%20imagined%20power%20and%20glory%20for%20the%20nation.%20Not%20accepting%20the%20demand%20or%20opposing%20it%20was%20portrayed%20as%20unpatriotic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n-300x175.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n-1024x596.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692049%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20supporters%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20Ayodhya.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FNarendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20missed%20every%20critic%E2%80%99s%20eye%20that%20the%20yatra%20secured%20the%20participation%20of%20different%20Hindu%20sects%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20during%20various%20religious%20congregations%2C%20inner%20contradictions%20and%20conflicts%20between%20the%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20Vaishnavites%2C%20Shaivites%2C%20Tantriks%20etc%2C%20were%20evident%20and%20clashes%20were%20common.%20This%20was%20evidence%20of%20future%20pan-Hindu%20unity%20but%20was%20also%20overlooked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%201980s%2C%20much%20water%20had%20flown%20down%20the%20rivers%20of%20India%2C%20especially%20Saryu%2C%20Yamuna%2C%20Gomti%20and%20Ganga%2C%20the%20four%20north%20Indian%20rivers%20that%20made%20its%20way%20past%20cities%20that%20became%20theatres%20of%20conflicts%20over%20the%20medieval%20shrine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20while%20other%20temple-mosque%20disputes%20were%20raked%20up%2C%20the%20Babri%20Masjid-Ram%20Janmabhomi%20temple%20conflict%20triggered%20several%20riots%20across%20regions%2C%20now%20home-base%20of%20Hindutva%20forces.%20Yet%2C%20a%20magical%20idea%20or%20a%20programme%20that%20could%20convert%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20temple%20a%20mass%20movement%20backed%20by%20large%20sections%20of%20Hindus%2C%20eluded%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%201987%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20began%20declining%2C%20his%20reputation%20as%20an%20incorruptible%20politician%20was%20besmirched%20and%20political%20support%20for%20VP%20Singh%20began%20widening.%20Amid%20increasing%20efforts%20at%20opposition%20unification%20as%20in%201977%2C%20the%20BJP%20made%20the%20Advanian%20choice%20of%20remaining%20in%20%E2%80%98splendid%20isolation%E2%80%99.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20backed%20anti-Congress%20agitations%20and%20even%20joined%20the%20Devi%20Lal-headed%20coalition%20government%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFast-forward%20to%201989%2C%20the%20year%20of%20the%20ninth%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20By%20then%20it%20was%20amply%20clear%20that%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20sword-arm%20on%20the%20Ayodhya%20movement%2C%20VHP%2C%20was%20lying%20in%20wait%20for%20an%20opportune%20moment%20to%20demolish%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20because%20the%20saffron%20clan%20functioned%20cohesively%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20fortunes%20could%20not%20be%20risked%20in%20the%20polls.%20Although%20it%20had%20just%20two%20seats%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20its%20leaders%20sensed%20that%20the%20a%20quantum%20jump%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20pitchfork%20the%20Ayodhya%20issue%20into%20the%20political%20centre-stage%2C%20the%20VHP%20announced%20two%20separate%20programmes.%20The%20first%20was%20the%20immensely%20controversial%20plan%20to%20lay%20the%20%E2%80%98foundation%20stone%E2%80%99%20or%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshila%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(brick%20or%20stone)%20at%20a%20chosen%20spot%20virtually%20in%20handshaking%20distance%20from%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20announced%20for%20November%209%2C%20also%20the%20day%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edevuththan%20ekadashi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(a%20Hindu%20festival%20when%20gods%20are%20believed%20to%20rise%20from%20celestial%20slumber)%20when%20pilgrims%20assembled%20in%20thousands%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20VHP%20and%20other%20affiliates%20of%20the%20RSS%20were%20tasked%20to%20mobilize%20support%20across%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20plan%20was%20a%20pan-Indian%20programme%20which%20eventually%20electrified%20large%20sections%20of%20Hindus%20and%20provided%20them%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98sense%20of%20participation%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20agitation%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple%20that%20was%20%E2%80%98destroyed%E2%80%99%20for%20building%20a%20mosque.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F02153242%2FThe-Outer-Inscription.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F02153242%2FThe-Outer-Inscription.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F02153242%2FThe-Outer-Inscription-300x191.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F02153242%2FThe-Outer-Inscription-1024x653.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-445694%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22765%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EInscription%20located%20outside%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20above%20its%20main%20entrance%20door.%20The%20inscription%20contains%208%20couplets%20of%20Persian%20verse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20campaign%2C%20specially%20manufactured%20bricks%2C%20euphemistically%20called%20Ram%20Shilas%2C%20were%20to%20be%20consecrated%20through%20special%20religious%20rituals%20in%20innumerable%20villages%2C%20colonies%2C%20towns%20and%20cities.%20Hindus%20were%20urged%20to%20participate%20in%20these%20rituals%20or%20line-up%20around%20the%20streets%20through%20which%20the%20bricks%20would%20wind%20their%20way%20to%20notified%20collections%20centres%20and%20eventually%20to%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20September%201989%20onward%2C%20the%20Ram%20Shilas%20were%20transported%20in%20trucks%2C%20escorted%20to%20Ayodhya%20by%20slogan-raising%20youth%20volunteers%20drawn%20from%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20The%20VHP%20declared%20that%20the%20shila%20%3Cem%3Epujan%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20was%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%20to%20Hindus%20at%20large.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20that%20happened%20or%20not%20remains%20a%20matter%20of%20dispute%2C%20but%20they%20surely%20caused%20communal%20riots%2C%20often%20triggered%20when%20VHP%20Ram%20Shila%20Yatras%20made%20their%20way%20provocatively%20through%20areas%20where%20Muslims%20dwelled%20in%20large%20numbers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20several%20lakh%20bricks%20eventually%20reached%20Ayodhya%20and%20multiples%20of%20these%20were%20used%20up%20by%20various%20people%20to%20construct%20private%20temples%20or%20other%20structures%20after%20making%20a%20%E2%80%98donation%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20cause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ram%20Shila%20Pujan%20and%20Yatra%20programme%20was%20the%20first%20major%20nationwide%20fund-collection%20drive%20of%20the%20VHP%20and%20this%20remained%20a%20steady%20feature%2C%20as%20in%202021%20when%20funds%20were%20raised%20for%20constructing%20the%20temple%20by%20activists%20of%20the%20RSS%20fraternity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fate%20of%20these%20bricks%20and%20almost%201.25%20lakh%20cubic%20feet%20of%20special%20stone%2C%20stored%20and%20carved%20in%20the%20locality%20which%20the%20VHP%20named%20Karsevakpuram%2C%20remains%20unknown%20although%20media%20reports%20mentioned%20that%20temple%20trustees%20had%20declared%20that%20these%20are%20being%20used%20in%20the%20construction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20claim%20however%2C%20is%20at%20variance%20of%20a%20sample%20test%20informally%20done%20by%20Central%20Building%20Research%20Institute%2C%20Roorkee%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%20The%20scientists%20had%20opined%20that%20the%20bricks%20could%20not%20be%20used%20in%20a%20single%20structure%20as%20they%20would%20expand%20and%20contract%20differently%20for%20having%20being%20made%20from%20soil%20of%20different%20regions.%20These%20details%20points%20to%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20tactics%20of%20devising%20campaigns%20which%20can%20mobile%20people%E2%80%99s%20support%20even%20though%20the%20intended%20objective%20may%20never%20be%20met%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20pray%20and%20offer%20donations%20for%20making%20bricks%20to%20be%20used%20for%20building%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESyed%20Shahabuddin%20was%20among%20the%20few%20Indian%20in%20politics%20and%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20characters%20of%20this%20macabre%20conflict%20that%20has%20still%20not%20ended%20playing%20out%20theatrically%20even%20after%20more%20than%20a%20century%20and%20a%20half%2C%20who%20sensed%20the%20enormous%20potential%20of%20the%20Ram%20Shila%20Pujan%20and%20Yatra%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthanks-to-the-ayodhya-judgment-faith-rather-than-fact-is-driving-indias-courts%5C%22%3EThanks%20to%20the%20Ayodhya%20Judgment%2C%20Faith%20Rather%20Than%20Fact%20is%20Driving%20India%E2%80%99s%20Courts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20this%20was%20announced%20during%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20in%20February%201989%2C%20this%20writer%20met%20him%20and%20shared%20the%20details%20of%20the%20announcement.%20His%20ashen%20expression%20as%20he%20heard%20and%20his%20response%20has%20not%20been%20forgotten%20for%20a%20moment%20since%20then%3A%20%E2%80%9CHereafter%20no%20one%20will%20be%20able%20to%20stop%20this%20mass%20movement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%2031%20years%20after%20the%20Shilanyas%20ceremony%2C%20barely%20a%20hundred%20odd%20feet%20away%20from%20the%20precincts%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20performed%20Bhoomi%20Pujan%20on%20August%205%2C%202020%20for%20the%20temple%20now%20still%20being%20built%20but%20will%20paradoxically%20be%20%E2%80%98consecrated%E2%80%99%20and%20inaugurated.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20day%20of%20the%20first%20anniversary%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07150038%2Fmodi-ayodhya-3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221053%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07150038%2Fmodi-ayodhya-3.png%201053w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07150038%2Fmodi-ayodhya-3-300x182.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07150038%2Fmodi-ayodhya-3-1024x621.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20along%20with%20UP%20governor%20Anandiben%20Patel%2C%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20and%20others%20perform%20Bhoomi%20Pujan%20rituals%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20at%20Ayodhya%20on%20August%205.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20one%20asked%20how%20Shilanyas%20was%20different%20from%20Bhoomi%20Pujan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20If%20another%20foundation%20stone%20was%20laid%20by%20Modi%2C%20what%20was%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20one%20laid%20by%20Kameshwar%20Chaupal%2C%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20member%20of%20the%20temple%20Trust%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20VHP%20activists%20and%20subsequently%20became%20a%20BJP%20legislator%20from%20Bihar%20for%20long%20before%20being%20handed%20his%20present%20job%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20been%20the%20standard%20pattern%20for%20almost%20three%20and%20a%20half%20decades%20since%20the%20Ram%20temple%20issue%20moved%20to%20the%20centre-stage%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20Repeating%20programmes%20and%20rituals%20was%20commonplace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAshok%20Singhal%2C%20the%20VHP%20strongman%20for%20decades%20and%20face%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20agitation%20prior%20to%20LK%20Advani%2C%20declared%20that%20the%20Shilanyas%20ceremony%20as%20performed%20by%20Chaupal%2C%20did%20not%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20just%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20but%20of%20a%20Hindu%20India.%20His%20assertion%20was%20articulated%20different%20by%20Advani%2C%20as%20aforementioned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndians%20shall%20wait%20for%20what%20Modi%20says%20after%20the%20ritual%20on%20January%2022%20and%20what%20would%20resonate%20thereafter.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20of%20November%202019%20generated%20hopes%20of%20a%20closure.%20Events%20since%20have%20proven%20that%20this%20remains%20elusive%2C%20in%20the%20present%2C%20or%20in%20the%20immediate%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sangh%20Parivar%2C%20now%20led%20by%20Modi%2C%20will%20continue%20%E2%80%98milking%E2%80%99%20Ram%20and%20the%20ideas%20birthed%20in%20the%20course%20of%20this%20agitation%20that%20has%20completely%20reconfigured%20India%2C%20for%20more%20political%20power%20and%20glory%20for%20more%20time%2C%20till%20the%20people%20see%20through%20this%20tactic%20when%20they%20are%20presented%20with%20an%20electoral%20opportunity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20several%20more%20copycat%20campaigns%20and%20similar%20turning%20points%2C%20it%20might%20be%20apt%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkashi-mathura-baaki-hain-why-the-ayodhya-verdict-wont-offer-any-respite-from-saffron-hatred%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EYeh%20to%20bas%20jhaanki%20hai%2C%20poori%20baat%20baaqi%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(this%20is%20a%20mere%20curtain-raiser%2C%20the%20entire%20tale%20remains%20to%20be%20told).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20author%2C%20and%20has%20written%20two%20books%20on%20the%20Babri%20Masjid-Ram%20temple%20dispute%2C%20one%20in%201994%20and%20the%20other%20in%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704717021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152731%2F415264154_1140688944092003_6108166337890878806_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ideas%20birthed%20in%20the%20course%20of%20this%20agitation%20have%20completely%20reconfigured%20India.%20But%20people%20will%20one%20day%20see%20through%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20court%20issues%20Imran%20Khan's%20release%20orders%20in%20Cypher%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704715696000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106640384%2Cimgsize-26602.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-issues-imran-khans-release-orders-in-cypher-case%2Farticleshow%2F106640278.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106640278.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Pakistan%20special%20court%20issued%20release%20orders%20for%20Imran%20Khan%20after%20his%20bail%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20Cypher%20case.%20Imran%20Khan%20will%20remain%20in%20Adiala%20Jail%20despite%20bail%20as%20he%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20a%20190%20million%20pounds%20case.%20The%20cypher%20case%20involves%20a%20diplomatic%20document%20that%20the%20Federal%20Investigation%20Agency%20alleges%20was%20never%20returned%20by%20Imran%2C%20with%20the%20PTI%20asserting%20the%20document%20contained%20a%20threat%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20remove%20Imran%20as%20prime%20minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-issues-imran-khans-release-orders-in-cypher-case%2Farticleshow%2F106640278.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-issues-imran-khans-release-orders-in-cypher-case%2Famp_articleshow%2F106640278.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-issues-imran-khans-release-orders-in-cypher-case%2Famp_articleshow%2F106640278.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DigiYatra%3A%20The%20Promise%20and%20Perils%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20New%20Airport%20Biometric%20System%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F13172957%2FUntitled-design-25.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%202023%20drew%20to%20a%20close%2C%20many%20Indians%20found%20themselves%20navigating%20the%20chaos%20of%20holiday%20travel.%20Overcrowded%20buses%20and%20trains%2C%20endless%20traffic%20jams%2C%20and%20exorbitantly%20priced%20flight%20tickets%20were%20the%20norms.%20Amid%20this%20seasonal%20tumult%2C%20a%20new%20challenge%20emerged%20for%20travellers%20at%20Indian%20airports%3A%20the%20%E2%80%98mandatory%E2%80%99%20implementation%20of%20DigiYatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDigiYatra%2C%20a%20biometric%20face%20scanning%20system%2C%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20and%20confusion%20among%20travellers.%20Many%20were%20uninformed%20about%20why%20their%20faces%20were%20being%20scanned%20or%20why%20participation%20was%20compulsory.%20This%20system%2C%20already%20operational%20in%2013%20airports%2C%20is%20set%20to%20expand%20nationwide%2C%20prompting%20urgent%20questions%20about%20its%20implications%20for%20privacy%2C%20data%20security%2C%20and%20civil%20liberties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20seasoned%20lawyer%20with%20deep%20insights%20into%20the%20intersection%20of%20technology%2C%20law%2C%20and%20civil%20rights%2C%20spearheads%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20called%20%E2%80%9C1984.%E2%80%9D%20The%20channel%2C%20named%20after%20George%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20dystopian%20novel%2C%20delves%20into%20the%20impact%20of%20digital%20technologies%20on%20democracy%20in%20India.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4DkLMc8faEk%26t%3D278s%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Erecent%20video%2C%20Gupta%20dissected%20the%20complexities%20of%20DigiYatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raising%20critical%20issues%20about%20its%20governance%2C%20data%20privacy%2C%20and%20potential%20for%20abuse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F4DkLMc8faEk%3Fsi%3DWSE5n0kHd7g_p73_%26start%3D299%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDigiYatra%20traces%20its%20origins%20back%20to%202018%2C%20with%20its%20primary%20objective%20being%20a%20seamless%2C%20contactless%20airport%20experience%20through%20facial%20recognition.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20claims%20that%20privacy%20concerns%20have%20been%20addressed%2C%20citing%20a%20decentralised%2C%20mobile%20wallet-based%20identity%20management%20system.%20However%2C%20Gupta%20expressed%20skepticism%2C%20pointing%20to%20significant%20gaps%20in%20these%20assurances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DigiYatra%20Foundation%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20established%20in%202019%2C%20administers%20the%20system.%20Its%20unique%20composition%20%E2%80%93%20a%20blend%20of%20public%20and%20private%20entities%20%E2%80%93%20complicates%20accountability.%20While%20the%20government%20holds%20a%2026%25%20stake%20through%20the%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20the%20rest%20is%20divided%20among%20major%20airports.%20This%20arrangement%2C%20Gupta%20argued%2C%20creates%20a%20quasi-monopolistic%20entity%20that%20lacks%20the%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20typically%20expected%20of%20public%20institutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20implementation%20model%20of%20DigiYatra%20raises%20questions%20about%20preferential%20treatment%20and%20the%20monetisation%20of%20passenger%20data.%20Gupta%20underscored%20the%20potential%20for%20airports%20to%20prioritise%20Digi%20Yatra%20users%2C%20thereby%20subtly%20coercing%20more%20travellers%20to%20opt%20into%20the%20system.%20The%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20model%2C%20which%20includes%20using%20passenger%20data%20for%20marketing%20hotels%2C%20taxis%2C%20and%20other%20services%2C%20further%20blurs%20the%20line%20between%20security%20and%20commercial%20exploitation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdigi-yatra-privacy-biometric-travel%5C%22%3EHow%20%E2%80%98Digi%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20Can%20Potentially%20Be%20Used%20To%20Police%20Your%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20privacy%20front%2C%20Gupta%20highlighted%20the%20absence%20of%20regulatory%20oversight%2C%20despite%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023.%20The%20act%E2%80%99s%20loopholes%20and%20the%20non-application%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20to%20the%20DigiYatra%20Foundation%20obscure%20the%20system%E2%80%99s%20data%20handling%20practices.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20public%20audits%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20data%20misuse%20raise%20alarms%20about%20the%20security%20of%20sensitive%20biometric%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%E2%80%99s%20critique%20extended%20beyond%20privacy%20concerns%2C%20touching%20on%20broader%20implications%20for%20democratic%20freedoms.%20He%20warns%20of%20a%20future%20where%20DigiYatra%20becomes%20a%20ubiquitous%20ID%2C%20required%20for%20everyday%20activities%20enabling%20pervasive%20state%20surveillance.%20This%20scenario%2C%20while%20speculative%2C%20is%20not%20unfounded%2C%20given%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20ambitions%20to%20expand%20DigiYatra%E2%80%99s%20applications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20Gupta%20called%20for%20public%20awareness%20and%20scrutiny.%20By%20sharing%20experiences%20and%20voicing%20concerns%2C%20citizens%20can%20challenge%20the%20encroaching%20reach%20of%20Digiyatra%20and%20demand%20transparency%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704715254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F13172957%2FUntitled-design-25.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdigiyatra-the-promise-and-perils-of-indias-new-airport-biometric-system%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20biometric%20face%20scanning%20system%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20and%20confusion%20among%20travellers.%20Many%20were%20uninformed%20about%20why%20their%20faces%20were%20being%20scanned%20or%20why%20participation%20was%20compulsory.%20This%20system%2C%20already%20operational%20in%2013%20airports%2C%20is%20set%20to%20expand%20nationwide%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fth