20coherent%20minority%20bloc.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20government%20has%20not%20viewed%20Muslims%20as%20a%20monolith%20but%20as%20wearing%20multiple%20identities.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslim%20women%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20vote%20bank%20or%20at%20least%20as%20those%20who%20needed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fa-year-later-are-instant-triple-talaq-culprits-actually-landing-in-jail%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98saving%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20triple%20talaq%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20recent%20qualitative%20surveys%20have%20shown%20that%20the%20law%20has%20presented%20a%20new%20set%20of%20challenges%20to%20Muslim%20women%2C%20and%20spawned%20several%20false%20criminal%20charges%20against%20men.%20Historically%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fpm-narendra-modi-lauds-bohra-community-for-peace-and-development%2Farticleshow%2F65816612.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20Bohri%20community%20has%20displayed%20admiration%20for%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20his%20days%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%20The%20community%20continues%20to%20be%20fervent%20admirers%20and%20are%20regularly%20seen%20in%20his%20diaspora%20events%20internationally.%20The%20government%20also%20showcased%20a%20successful%20Muharram%20procession%20by%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shias%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20normalcy%20in%20the%20Valley%20post%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%20Modi%20has%20bifurcated%20the%20Muslim%20community%20into%20these%20favourable%20groupings%20of%20potential%20allies%20rather%20than%20ignoring%20them%20as%20a%20lost%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnot-in-our-name-over-3000-christians-dissociate-from-pm-modis-christmas-lunch%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20in%20Our%20Name%E2%80%99%3A%20Over%203%2C000%20Christians%20Dissociate%20From%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Christmas%20Lunch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20purpose%20does%20this%20serve%20for%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20certainly%20does%20not%20need%20the%20additional%20minority%20vote%20bank%2C%20but%20it%20has%20multiple%20benefits.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20it%20matters%20for%20his%20narrative%20and%20projection%20to%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20despite%20whatever%20his%20rabble-rouser%20election%20spokespeople%20say%20and%20do.%20The%20image%20of%20a%20free%2C%20multi-cultural%2C%20secular%20India%20must%20be%20projected%20in%20the%20international%20world.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20provides%20the%20BJP%20vote%20bank%20with%20a%20few%20cherry-picked%20niceties%20to%20showcase%20that%20Modi%20is%20loved%20by%20all%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20propaganda%20that%20displays%20anything%20to%20the%20contrary.%20Thirdly%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20may%20or%20may%20not%20get%20a%20sizeable%20winning%20vote%20bank%20from%20this%20outreach%2C%20it%20helps%20it%20prevent%20the%20wholesale%20transfer%20of%20these%20votes%20en%20bloc%20to%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20for%20these%20hand-picked%20minorities%20who%20do%20not%20mind%20playing%20to%20the%20gallery%2C%20it%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20the%20chosen%20few%20who%20are%20favoured%20by%20the%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20opposition%20is%20caught%20between%20being%20soft%20or%20visibly%20Hindu%2C%20it%20has%20chosen%20to%20take%20the%20minorities%20for%20granted.%20Minorities%20have%20languished%20without%20effective%20bargaining%20power%20because%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20survival%2C%20their%20options%20remain%20limited%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20opposition.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20true%20loser%20in%20this%20debate%20is%20the%20average%20minority%20citizen.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20changing%20political%20space%2C%20minority%20votes%20are%20not%20openly%20courted%20as%20kingmakers.%20And%20in%20cases%20where%20they%20are%2C%20the%20opposition%20is%20faced%20with%20new%20dilemmas.%20In%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20released%20a%20minority%20declaration%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20swinging%20these%20votes%2C%20which%20it%20may%20just%20have.%20However%2C%20it%20faces%20a%20new%20crisis%20as%20it%20has%20no%20Muslim%20MLA.%20All%20its%20Muslim%20candidates%20lost%20the%20election.%20Without%20a%20voice%20from%20the%20government%20in%20the%20legislature%2C%20it%20must%20resort%20to%20nominating%20a%20Muslim%20to%20the%20Telangana%20Legislative%20Council.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-india-alliance-rahul-gandhi-2024%5C%22%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20Nothing%20%E2%80%98Inevitable%E2%80%99%20About%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Return%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMinorities%20in%20India%20continue%20to%20lag%20on%20most%20socio-economic%20indicators%20and%20face%20communal%20toxicity%20everyday.%20Yet%2C%20the%20BJP%20touts%20its%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESabka%20Saath%20Sabka%20Vikas%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20model.%20In%20certain%20government%20schemes%2C%20minorities%20like%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20receive%20a%20slightly%20larger%20proportion%20of%20benefits%20than%20their%20proportion%20of%20the%20population.%20In%202021%2C%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20claimed%20that%20Muslims%20who%20comprise%2017%25-18%25%20of%20the%20population%20disproportionately%20make-up%2034%25-35%25%20of%20beneficiaries%20of%20BJP%20governments%E2%80%99%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20thus%20demonstrating%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20benevolence.%20However%2C%20this%20actually%20demonstrates%20the%20disproportionate%20weaker%20economic%20status%20of%20Muslims%20owing%20to%20years%20of%20marginalisation%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20dominant%20myth%20of%20minority%20appeasement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20intent%20becomes%20clearer%20when%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20reduction%20of%20targeted%20and%20specific%20policies.%20In%20the%202023%20budget%2C%20a%20whopping%2038%25%20was%20slashed%20from%20the%20minority%20affairs%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20allocation.%20Yet%2C%20we%20live%20in%20a%20make-believe%20of%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20for%20all%2C%20appeasement%20of%20none%E2%80%9D.%20Also%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20to%20be%20readying%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20which%20had%20triggered%20nationwide%20protests%20especially%20from%20minorities%20that%20were%20curtailed%20only%20because%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Modi%20continues%20to%20embrace%20his%20chosen%20minorities%2C%20and%20his%20rabble-rousers%20continue%20to%20intimidate%20and%20spread%20discord%2C%20the%20opposition%20too%20is%20failing%20to%20piece%20together%20a%20coherent%20strategy.%20What%20minorities%20need%20is%20neither%20appeasement%20nor%20benevolence%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%20where%20they%20can%20participate%20in%20decision-making.%20Meaningful%20representation%20involves%20allowing%20minority%20concerns%20to%20be%20raised%20and%20addressed%20effectively.%20Lest%20minorities%20are%20left%20with%20searching%20for%20their%20version%20of%20the%20BJP%20within%20their%20own%20religious%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmaan%20Asim%20graduated%20from%20Ashoka%20University%20with%20a%20major%20in%20political%20science%20and%20is%20a%20political%20consultant%20to%20leaders%20across%20multiple%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704708007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30194902%2FEffect-49.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-bjps-outreach-to-minority-communities-mean-for-the-opposition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20may%20or%20may%20not%20get%20a%20sizeable%20winning%20vote%20bank%20from%20this%20outreach%2C%20but%20it%20may%20help%20it%20prevent%20the%20wholesale%20transfer%20of%20these%20votes%20en%20bloc%20to%20the%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-bjps-outreach-to-minority-communities-mean-for-the-opposition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tractors%20block%20roads%20as%20German%20farmers%20protest%20over%20diesel%20tax%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704707280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-berlin-farmers-germany_6414724.jpg%3F20240108100215%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgerman-farmers-block-roads-in-nationwide-protest-over-diesel-tax-plans-13043996%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22German%20farmers%20have%20blocked%20roads%20with%20tractors%20and%20trucks%20as%20they%20start%20a%20week%20of%20protests%20over%20plans%20to%20scrap%20tax%20breaks%20on%20diesel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A323%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgerman-farmers-block-roads-in-nationwide-protest-over-diesel-tax-plans-13043996%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgerman-farmers-block-roads-in-nationwide-protest-over-diesel-tax-plans-13043996%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgerman-farmers-block-roads-in-nationwide-protest-over-diesel-tax-plans-13043996%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moon%20mission%20carries%20sports%20drink%20and%20human%20remains%20-%20is%20this%20compatible%20with%20science%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704707100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-rocket-mission_6414555.jpg%3F20240108065539%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fperegrine-moon-mission-carries-sports-drink-and-human-remains-is-this-compatible-with-science-13043993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA%20is%20on%20its%20way%20back%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20but%20this%20time%20it's%20not%20at%20the%20controls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A189%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fperegrine-moon-mission-carries-sports-drink-and-human-remains-is-this-compatible-with-science-13043993%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fperegrine-moon-mission-carries-sports-drink-and-human-remains-is-this-compatible-with-science-13043993%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fperegrine-moon-mission-carries-sports-drink-and-human-remains-is-this-compatible-with-science-13043993%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Unites%20the%20Air%20of%20Asia's%20Cities%3F%20An%20Invisible%20Killer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08131855%2FScreenshot-2024-01-08-at-1.18.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20deaths%20increase%20by%20150%2C000%20in%20rapidly%20growing%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20people%20in%20cities%20in%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20face%20the%20threat%20of%20dying%20prematurely%20due%20to%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighteen%20cities%20in%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20tropical%20region%20are%20growing%20fast%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20home%20to%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F0956247816663557%5C%22%3E10%20million%20people%20each%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%202100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20have%20limited%20to%20no%20routine%20ground%20monitoring%20of%20air%20pollution%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20work%20out%20how%20bad%20the%20air%20has%20become%20resulting%20from%20this%20rapid%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20increase%20due%20to%20insufficient%20control%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20inadequate%20funding%20for%20monitoring%20pollutants%20such%20as%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20and%20ammonia%20that%20also%20form%20harmful%20fine%20particles%20(PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20hazardous%20pollutant%20of%20them%20all%20is%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%2C%20which%20penetrates%20deep%20into%20the%20lungs%20and%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20impact%20just%20about%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournal.chestnet.org%2Farticle%2FS0012-3692(18)32723-5%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Eevery%20organ%20in%20the%20human%20body%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Long-term%20exposure%20to%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.abm4435%5C%22%3Ewas%20linked%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20149%2C000%20early%20deaths%20in%20South%20Asian%20cities%20and%2053%2C000%20in%20Southeast%20Asian%20cities%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20increased%20by%20126%2C000%20to%20275%2C000%20in%20South%20Asian%20cities%20and%20by%2026%2C000%20to%2080%2C000%20in%20Southeast%20Asian%20cities%20in%202018.%20Dhaka%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Mumbai%20and%20Bangalore%20in%20India%20had%20the%20largest%20increase%20in%20early%20deaths%20from%20long-term%20exposure%20to%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20increase%20in%20early%20deaths%20in%20South%20Asian%20cities%20is%20the%20combined%20result%20of%20both%20increasing%20populations%20and%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0levels%20from%202005%20to%202018.%20For%20cities%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20population%20increase%20played%20a%20much%20larger%20role%20in%20the%20increase%20than%20change%20in%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%20of%20the%20study%2C%20which%20focused%20only%20on%20the%20tropical%20region%2C%20suggest%20that%20even%20if%20the%20air%20pollution%20levels%20remain%20the%20same%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20urban%20population%20in%20these%20fast-growing%20cities%20will%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20exposure%20to%20harmful%20pollutants%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20early%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20anticipated%20rapid%20urban%20expansion%20throughout%20this%20century%2C%20the%20issue%20could%20be%20exacerbated%20unless%20new%20measures%20are%20implemented%20to%20mitigate%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20increased%20interest%20in%20low-cost%20sensors%2C%20these%20are%20prone%20to%20biases%20and%20are%20relatively%20recent%20and%20so%20do%20not%20provide%20information%20about%20the%20changes%20in%20air%20pollution%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstruments%20on%20board%20satellites%20are%20the%20eyes%20in%20the%20skies%20which%20provide%20a%20long%20record%20and%20an%20extensive%20coverage%20of%20air%20pollution.%20Data%20from%20space-based%20instruments%20is%20publicly%20available%20for%20a%20suite%20of%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20effective%20these%20satellite%20observations%20are%20for%20monitoring%20air%20pollution%20in%20cities%20has%20been%20well%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facp.copernicus.org%2Farticles%2F21%2F6275%2F2021%2F%5C%22%3Eevaluated%20against%20ground-based%20monitors%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0where%20these%20are%20available%2C%20prompting%20greater%20use%20of%20satellites%20where%20ground-based%20monitoring%20is%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.abm4435%5C%22%3ESatellite%20observations%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0collected%20between%202005%20and%202018%20by%20NASA%20and%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20show%20increasing%20levels%20of%20most%20air%20pollutants%20across%20the%2018%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20study%2C%20the%20cities%20analysed%20were%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bangalore%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Chittagong%2C%20Dhaka%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Karachi%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%20and%20Surat%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20Bangkok%2C%20Hanoi%2C%20Ho%20Chi%20Minh%20City%2C%20Jakarta%2C%20Manila%2C%20Phnom%20Penh%20and%20Yangon%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20cities%20in%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20show%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20that%20directly%20impacts%20health%2C%20along%20with%20forming%20health-hazardous%20ozone%20and%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitrogen%20dioxide%20levels%20tripled%20in%20Chittagong%20(Bangladesh)%20and%20doubled%20in%20Dhaka%20(Bangladesh)%20and%20Hanoi%20(Vietnam)%20over%20the%2014-year%20period.%20These%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20increase%20in%20emissions%20from%20vehicular%20traffic%20and%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJakarta%20in%20Indonesia%20is%20the%20only%20city%20with%20a%20decline%20in%20nitrogen%20dioxide%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20success%20of%20air%20quality%20measures%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.academia.edu%2F1362194%2FEvaluating_the_Effects_of_a_New_Vehicle_Emission_Standard_on_Urban_Air_Quality_in_Jakarta_City%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20in%202005%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgricultural%20emissions%20linked%20to%20livestock%20and%20fertilisers%20are%20typically%20unregulated%20and%20are%20the%20dominant%20sources%20of%20ammonia%2C%20a%20respiratory%20irritant%20which%20is%20also%20a%20precursor%20of%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20ammonia%20from%20urban%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreases%20in%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20and%20ammonia%20levels%20drive%20the%20increases%20in%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%20There%20is%20a%20large%20and%20significant%20increase%20of%20up%20to%208%20percent%20each%20year%20in%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0levels%20in%20Indian%20cities%20with%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0increasing%20to%20more%20than%20double%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20Hyderabad%20from%202005%20to%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20observations%20are%20at%20a%20very%20coarse%20resolution%20of%20about%20tens%20of%20kilometres%20and%20with%20limited%20ground%20monitoring%2C%20air%20pollution%20sources%20can%20only%20be%20speculated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20centuries%2C%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20have%20grappled%20with%20air%20pollution%20primarily%20stemming%20from%20the%20widespread%20practice%20of%20open%20burning%20of%20agricultural%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20commonly%20burn%20vegetation%20during%20the%20dry%20season%20to%20clear%20land%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20upcoming%20sowing%20season.%20The%20smoke%20from%20these%20fires%20is%20laden%20with%20pollutants%2C%20posing%20risks%20to%20both%20human%20health%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20looking%20at%20cities%2C%20where%20most%20people%20live%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shift%20from%20rural%20to%20urban%20sources%20of%20pollution%20such%20as%20road%20traffic%20and%20burning%20of%20waste%20and%20household%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20mitigation%20measures%20are%20one%20of%20the%20challenges%20facing%20Asian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20encompass%20enhanced%20ground%20monitoring%20capabilities%20to%20pinpoint%20local%20sources%20of%20air%20pollution%2C%20as%20well%20as%20regulating%20uncontrolled%20emissions%20such%20as%20those%20from%20agriculture%2C%20which%20contribute%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20more%20harmful%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accessibility%20of%20emission%20control%20technologies%20has%20become%20more%20affordable%20and%20easier%20than%20ever.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20learn%20from%20past%20mistakes%20and%20take%20action%20now%20to%20prevent%20an%20imminent%20health%20crisis%20in%20these%20rapidly%20growing%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDr%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ucl.ac.uk%2Fgeography%2Fkarn-vohra%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EKarn%20Vohra%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Research%20Fellow%20at%20University%20College%20London.%20He%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20Environmental%20Health%20and%20Risk%20Management%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Birmingham.%20His%20research%20focuses%20on%20the%20application%20of%20ground-based%20and%20satellite%20observations%2C%20chemical%20transport%20models%20and%20health%20risk%20assessment%20models%20to%20improve%20the%20understanding%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20its%20sources%20on%20public%20health.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHe%20received%20funding%20for%20his%20research%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Birmingham%20Global%20Challenges%20Studentship.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0by%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%84%A2.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704706255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08131855%2FScreenshot-2024-01-08-at-1.18.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwhat-unites-the-air-of-asias-cities-an-invisible-killer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accessibility%20of%20emission%20control%20technologies%20has%20become%20more%20affordable%20and%20easier%20than%20ever.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20learn%20from%20past%20mistakes%20and%20take%20action%20now%20to%20prevent%20an%20imminent%20health%20crisis%20in%20these%20rapidly%20growing%20cities.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en