Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20and%20man%E2%80%99s%20mothers%20are%20sisters%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20and%20have%20married%20into%20different%20faiths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20victim%20girl%20is%20a%20graduate%20and%20she%20visited%20her%20college%20to%20collect%20some%20documents.%20She%20was%20told%20to%20wait%20till%203.30%20pm.%20Meanwhile%2C%20her%20cousin%20joined%20her%20and%20both%20were%20waiting%20at%20the%20Lake%20Park.%20As%20the%20girl%20was%20covering%20her%20face%20with%20a%20hijab%20and%20the%20boy%20was%20sporting%20a%20tilak%2C%20the%20accused%20thought%20that%20they%20were%20lovers%20and%20attacked%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mob%20took%20the%20two%20to%20an%20isolated%20location%20and%20repeatedly%20assaulted%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20repeatedly%20told%20them%20that%20Rahul%20(name%20changed)%20is%20my%20cousin%20but%20none%20listened%20to%20me.%20They%20snatched%20our%20mobile%20phones.%20They%20took%20him%20to%20another%20room%20and%20assaulted%20him.%20They%20also%20hit%20me%20asking%20why%20I%20was%20roaming%20around%20with%20a%20Hindu%20boy%20being%20a%20Muslim%20girl%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20woman%20has%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assault%20ended%20three%20hours%20later%20only%20because%20the%20man%20somehow%20managed%20to%20dial%20the%20police%20number.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20booked%20the%20accused%20under%20Sections%20307%20(attempt%20to%20murder)%2C%20149%20(unlawful%20assembly)%2C%20394%20(robbery)%2C%20324%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt%20by%20dangerous%20weapons%20or%20means)%2C%20and%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Mohammad%20Ayman%2C%2027%2C%20Hussain%2C%2022%2C%20Ateef%2C%2022%2C%20Saif%20Ali%2C%2027%2C%20Umar%2C%2018%2C%20Rehan%2C%2019%2C%20and%20Azan%2C%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704704406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18112127%2FFF69BF43-2716-4AC6-8E67-457755F26570.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcousins-allegedly-assaulted-in-karnataka-after-mob-assumes-they-are-an-interfaith-couple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nine%20of%20the%2017%20accused%20%E2%80%93%20including%20two%20minors%20%E2%80%93%20are%20now%20reportedly%20in%20police%20custody.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcousins-allegedly-assaulted-in-karnataka-after-mob-assumes-they-are-an-interfaith-couple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20in%201992%3A%20%E2%80%98What%20Happened%20on%20December%206%20at%20Ayodhya%20Should%20Not%20Have%20Happened%20at%20All'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08111807%2FScreenshot-2024-01-08-at-11.17.13-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%2C%20from%20our%20series%20%3C%2Fem%3EFlashback%20Ayodhya%3A%20How%20the%20Plot%20Unfolded%3Cem%3E%2C%20is%20a%20transcript%20of%20an%20interview%20which%20was%20published%20first%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3EEyewitness%3Cem%3E%2C%20in%20the%20January%201993%20edition%20of%20the%20video%20newsmagazine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMr.%20Vajpayee%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20often%20been%20described%20as%20a%20liberal.%20What%20does%20a%20liberal%20mean%20to%20you%3F%20What%20are%20the%20sort%20of%20liberal%20values%20that%20you%20hold%20dear%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20tolerance.%20Even%20if%20you%20think%20that%20the%20other%20viewpoint%2