ort%20us.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20YouTubers.%20We%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20locations%20available%20in%20our%20village%20to%20tell%20a%20simple%20story.%20We%20have%20a%20railway%20station%2C%20a%20canal%20like%20river%2C%20greenery%2C%20jungle%2C%20colleges%2C%20schools%2C%20police%20stations.%20Every%20household%20in%20the%20village%20is%20part%20of%20our%20studio%3B%20just%20take%20permission%20and%20shoot.%20Everyone%20is%20supportive%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Jay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2059-year-old%20resident%20of%20the%20village%2C%20Pyarelal%20Verma%2C%20regularly%20acts%20in%20their%20videos.%20Playing%20age-appropriate%20roles%2C%20he%20enjoys%20participating%20in%20the%20shoots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20videos%20are%20uploaded%2C%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world%20watch%20them.%20Our%20relatives%20and%20friends%20from%20places%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20even%20from%20abroad%20call%20us%20to%20appreciate%20our%20work.%20They%20are%20proud%20of%20us.%20Sometimes%20we%20meet%20strangers%20who%20recognise%20us%2C%20talk%20to%20us%2C%20and%20are%20delighted%20to%20meet%20us.%20They%20say%20we%20are%20bringing%20glory%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F245586%2Fifs-hero-chhattisgarh-adivasi-dfo-ganveer-dhammshil-transfer-tribal-community-protest-forest-officer-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20culture%20and%20to%20our%20village%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20the%20greatest%20reward%20for%20the%20innovative%20efforts%20here%20in%20Tulsi%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETulsi%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20shows%20the%20potential%20of%20small%20towns%20and%20villages%20and%20proves%20that%20progress%20isn%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20large%20metropolises.%20Large%20number%20of%C2%A0%20residents%20of%20Tulsi%2C%20from%2015-year-olds%20to%20an%2085-year-old%20woman%2C%20all%