%3EKufri%20Neelkanth%3C%2Fem%3E%20potato%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20purple%20often%20indicates%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291624%2Fmillets-help-in-weight-loss-delicious-recipes-health-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresence%20of%20nutrients%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20anthocyanins.%20Like%20other%20phytonutrients%2C%20your%20body%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20them%20to%20function%2C%20but%20they%20do%20help%20protect%20your%20cells%20from%20damage%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20illness%20and%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20potatoes%20are%20probably%20rich%20in%20anthocyanins%2C%20imparting%20a%20deep%20purple%20colour.%20A%20class%20of%20flavonoids%2C%20anthocyanins%20are%20known%20to%20have%20several%20health%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cftri.res.in%2FProfile%2F0_37803600_1534424669.pdf%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Pradeep%20Singh%20Negi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%2C%20Fruit%20and%20Vegetable%20Technology%20Department%20at%20Mysore-based%20CSIR-Central%20Food%20Technological%20Research%20Institute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20hues%20from%20blue%20to%20red%2C%20anthocyanins%20are%20water-soluble%20and%20are%20used%20as%20food%20colourant%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20potato%20varieties%20impact%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20because%20of%20their%20carbohydrate%20content%2C%20black%20potatoes%20may%20exert%20less%20of%20an%20effect%20than%20other%20types%20due%20to%20their%20high%20concentration%20of%20polyphenol%20plant%20compounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20anthocyanins%2C%20they%20have%202-3%20times%20the%20total%20antioxidants%20of%20a%20typical%20white%20potato%2C%20which%20is%20loaded%20with%20potassium%2C%20magnesium%2C%20vitamin%20C%2C%20and%20fibre.%20Fruits%20such%20as%20jamun%2C%20blueberries%2C%20and%20blackberries%20are%20rich%20in%20anthocyanins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glycemic%20index%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fnutrition%2Fpurple-potatoes%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520glycemic%2520index%2520(GI)%2520is%2CGI%2520of%252093%2520(%25205%2520).%5C%22%3E(GI)%20measures%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20food%20raises%20your%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20ranges%20from%200%20to%20100%2C%20and%20a%20GI%20greater%20than%2070%20is%20considered%20high.%20A%20comparison%20study%20in%20humans%20found%20that%20black%20potatoes%20have%20a%20GI%20of%2077%2C%20yellow%20potatoes%20have%20a%20GI%20of%2081%2C%20and%20white%20potatoes%20have%20a%20GI%20of%2093.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBlack-potatoes-1704205878.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20full-size%20black%20potatoes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBlack-potatoes-1704205878.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBlack-potatoes-1704205878-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBlack-potatoes-1704205878-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBlack-potatoes-1704205878-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBlack-potatoes-1704205878-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20full-size%20black%20potatoes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20popular%20is%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20new%20variety%2C%20most%20farmers%20are%20still%20experimenting%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farmers%20order%20between%203-5%20kg%20of%20seeds.%20They%20keep%20parts%20of%20the%20harvest%20for%20themselves%20and%20the%20rest%20to%20sell%20as%20tubers%20or%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maurya.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20main%20reason%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20see%20it%20in%20the%20markets%20or%20shops.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Abhishek%20Shrivastava%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Agri%20Junction%20%E2%80%94%20an%20initiative%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20with%204%2C000%20outlets%20across%20the%20state%20%E2%80%94%20put%20up%20a%20video%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfxFxum_0i6o%26ab_channel%3DAGRIJUNCTION%5C%22%3EYoutube%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%202020%20about%20the%20black%20potatoes%2C%20he%20has%20been%20flooded%20with%20requests%20for%20these%20tubers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20supplied%20a%20total%20of%203%2C000%20kg%20of%20these%20to%20farmers%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20early%202025%2C%20we%20will%20hopefully%20see%20black%20potatoes%20arriving%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shrivastava.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20flooded%20with%20orders%20for%20the%20tubers%20and%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20supplied%20it%20to%20more%20than%20500%20plus%20farmers%20across%20the%20country.%20He%20even%20experimented%20and%20made%20potato%20chips%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F243679%2Fkerala-covid-19-lockdown-woman-starts-home-business-papad-jackfruit-coconut-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epapad%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20home%20from%20the%20vegetable.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20may%20be%20dark%20in%20colour%20but%20are%20very%20tasty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamgopal%20Chandel%20of%20Barsawan%20village%20has%20been%20growing%20black%20potatoes%20on%20one%20bigha%20land%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20now.%C2%A0%20Having%20spent%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20on%20inputs%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20get%20around%2080%20quintals%20per%20bigha%2C%20which%20is%20slightly%20less%20than%20the%20regular%20ones.%20But%20this%20potato%20scores%20well%20as%20its%20shelf%20life%20is%20longer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20try%20out%20this%20vegetable%20for%20your%20garden%20or%20kitchen%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Ravi%20Prakash%20Maurya%20at%209026253336.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704207927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravi%20Prakash%20Maurya%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20cultivating%20%E2%80%98black%20crops%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20rice%2C%20wheat%2C%20tomato%2C%20niger%20seeds%2C%20turmeric%20and%20potato%20%E2%80%94%20all%20with%20one%20thing%20in%20common%2C%20their%20colour%20and%20presence%20of%20antioxidants.%20Here's%20why%20he's%20promoting%20black%20potatoes%20across%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hiren%20Kumar%20Bose%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A244%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337247%2Fblack-potato-kaala-aaloo-shetland-farmer-in-uttar-pradesh-antioxidants%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20New%20Year%2C%20Volunteer%20With%202%20Friends%20Who%20Have%20Cleared%20450000%20Kg%20Waste%20Off%20a%20Mumbai%20Beach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mumbai%20resident%20Kunti%20Oza%20was%20younger%2C%20beach%20days%20meant%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308332%2Fkerala-beaches-lesser-known-travel-destinations-varkala-thikkodi-kolavi-munambam-kuzhuppilly%2F%5C%2